ractical%20for%20everyday%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inference%20of%20large%20language%20models%20is%20incredibly%20computationally%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-intelligence-compatibility-iphone-models-mac-ipad-ios-18-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20newest%20A17%20chips%20are%20so%20well%20suited%20for%20the%20task%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20oomph%20in%20the%20device%20to%20actually%20do%20these%20models%20fast%20enough%20to%20be%20useful.%20You%20could%20in%20theory%20run%20these%20models%20on%20a%20very%20old%20device%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20so%20slow%20will%20not%20be%20useful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20getting%20the%20technical%20parameters%20right%2C%20Giannandrea%20said%20his%20team%20is%20also%20wrestling%20with%20philosophical%20and%20ethical%20questions%20about%20the%20role%20AI%20will%20play%20in%20people's%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20very%20careful%20about%20applying%20this%20technology%20in%20a%20very%20thoughtful%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20tried%20to%20corral%20this%20technology%20to%20do%20what%20it's%20really%20good%20at%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20even%20though%20researchers%20are%20concerned%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20safety%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Giannandrea%20said%20Apple%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20limiting%20the%20creativity%20of%20its%20users%20with%20an%20overly%20restrictive%20set%20of%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20fine%20balance%20as%20we%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20years%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20because%20this%20is%20new%20for%20us.%20This%20is%20new%20for%20the%20whole%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-ai-chief-w