20different%20industries%2C%20especially%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20heard%20people%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-work-fashion-tips-stylists-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20doesn't%20know%20how%20to%20dress%20for%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20true%20%E2%80%94%20we%20just%20do%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290963d32-e3ea-42d0-9267-e9d1aae7443e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGen%20Z%20prioritizes%20self-expression%2C%20and%20that%20extends%20beyond%20their%20personal%20lives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20girl%20takes%20a%20photo%20standing%20on%20the%20sidewalk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667091f1e07904901819bdcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPenn.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Maya%20Penn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-envy-gen-z-ability-to-say-no-in-workplace-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20is%20challenging%20the%20standards%20of%20the%20business%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20want%20to%20bring%20our%20own%20style%20and%20personality%20into%20every%20space%20we%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20been%20important%20for%20me%20to%20stand%20out%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20had%20my%20own%20style.%20I've%20never%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20adhere%20to%20specific%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20fashion%20is%20fun%20and%20quirky%2C%20and%20we're%20into%20self-expression.%20We%20want%20to%20show%20more%20color%20and%20creativity%20and%20be%20more%20nontraditional%20in%20our%20clothing.%20You're%20less%20likely%20to%20see%20us%20in%20whatever%20runway%20models%20are%20wearing%20and%20more%20likely%20to%20see%20us%20incorporating%20our%20favorite%20anime%20characters%20and%20other%20interests%20into%20how%20we