sses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20next%20to%20a%20TED%20Talk%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66709109764df161125a85cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPenn%20at%20TEDWomen.%3Cp%3EGilberto%20Tadday%20%2F%20TEDWomen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20amazing%20vintage%20shops%20on%20Etsy%20and%20Instagram.%20I%20also%20support%20local%20thrift%20stores%20and%20love%20wearing%20my%20mom's%20clothing%20or%20jewelry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae15315b-79be-47aa-b6b4-4035978459f2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20also%20really%20into%20tailoring%20and%20mending%20clothes%20and%20accessories%20to%20give%20them%20a%20new%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20sustainable%20fashion%20is%20what's%20already%20in%20your%20closet.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-fashion-environmental-impact-pollution-emissions-waste-water-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFast-fashion%20clothing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20worn%20only%2010%20times%20before%20it%20starts%20falling%20apart.%20I%20actively%20avoid%20fast-fashion%20labels%2C%20but%20if%20I%20buy%20new%20clothes%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20from%20small%2C%20local%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20tailor%20my%20own%20outfits%20when%20needed%2C%20but%20tailoring%20services%20are%20available%20everywhere.%20Having%20a%20greener%20wardrobe%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20need%20to%20sacrifice%20self-expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b00fb7a-0953-4e14-85f4-9d7de6c49357%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20like%20to%20play%20with%20traditional%20elements%20of%20corporate%20style%20but%20incorporate%20elements%20of%20my%20creative%20side%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20takes%20a%20mirror%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66709184ed9a404d829e770a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPenn.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Maya%20Penn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20outfits%20is%20a%20power%20suit%20or%20blazer%20mixed%20with%20artsy%20pieces.%20I'm%20not%20one%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20color%2C%20so%20I%20might%20combine%20it%20with%20something%20really%20bright%20or%20some%20eclectic%20jewelry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20also%20want%20to%20challenge%20the%20business%20world%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20I'm%20even%20more%20comfortable%20combining%20business%20wear%20with%20prints%20and%20jewelry%20from%20the%20African%20and%20Indigenous%20diaspora%20and%20weaving%20the%20different%20elements%20of%20who%20I%20am%20into%20what%20I%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba4a20df-302e-43cc-8410-2e531d147209%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20gotten%20some%20negative%20responses%20to%20the%20way%20I%20look%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20is%20redefining%20professionalism%20more%20inclusively%2C%20allowing%20for%20the%20expression%20of%20identities%20and%20cultural%20backgrounds.%20However%2C%20there's%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20progress%20to%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20negative%20response%20that%20I've%20gotten%20to%20my%20look%20is%20about%20my%20natural%20Afro.%20I've%20received%20comments%20about%20this%20from%20adults%20since%20I%20was%20a%20child.%20When%20asked%20about%20it%2C%20I%20respond%20that%20yes%2C%20it's%20my%20natural%20hair%2C%20and%20I%20wear%20it%20this%20way%20because%20it's%20beautiful%2C%20elegant%2C%20and%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20states%20still%20haven't%20passed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecrownact.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20CROWN%20(Create%20a%20Respectful%20and%20Open%20Workplace%20for%20Natural%20Hair)%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20first%20signed%20into%20California%20law%20in%202019.%20The%20CROWN%20Act%20aims%20to%20protect%20people%20from%20discrimination%20about%20race-based%20hairstyles%20by%20extending%20statutory%20protection%20to%20hair%20texture%20and%20protective%20styles%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20braids%2C%20locs%2C%20twists%2C%20and%20knots%20%E2%80%94%20in%20workplaces%20and%20public%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c8f1dab-f7a5-4d7e-9cb6-1aed6277c8ac%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20set%20a%20dress%20code%20in%20my%20businesses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20my%20businesses%20intersect%20with%20creative%20industries%2C%20and%20I%20want%20my%20employees%20to%20be%20able%20to%20express%20themselves.%20People%20in%20my%20industry%20tend%20to%20have%20colorful%20or%20eclectic%20ways%20of%20dress%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20older%20generations%20want%20to%20dress%20in%20more%20traditional%20business%20attire%2C%20it's%20none%20of%20my%20business.%20People%20should%20be%20able%20to%20wear%20whatever%20they%20want.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20by%20recycling%20fashion%20from%20past%20generations%2C%20we're%20not%20that%20far%20removed%20from%20their%20aesthetics%20%E2%80%94%20we%20just%20have%20different%20outlooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20matters%20to%20me%20is%20that%20my%20employees%20are%20professional%2C%20they%20do%20the%20work%20and%20meet%20deadlines%2C%20and%20they%20treat%20people%20around%20them%20with%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20can%20do%20all%20that%20but%20want%20to%20come%20to%20work%20with%20pink%20hair%20and%20piercings%2C%20that's%20fine%20by%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-professional-wears-afro-bold-clothes-work-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718701501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66708632e07904901819b6f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2