is%20new%20role%2C%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20was%20faced%20with%20multiple%20strikes%20impacting%20film%20and%20TV%20production.%20Ayaz%20helped%20the%20company%20navigate%20these%20challenges%20while%20also%20driving%20the%20global%20campaign%20to%20celebrate%20Disney's%20100th%20anniversary%2C%20which%20had%20kicked%20off%20with%20a%20Super%20Bowl%20commercial%20in%202023%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20new%20logo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20Ayaz%20pioneered%20new%20partnerships%20and%20social%20campaigns%20to%20bring%20the%20effort%20to%20a%20diverse%20set%20of%20audiences.%20Ayaz%20led%20a%20collaboration%20with%20TikTok%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20introduce%20a%20Disney100%20hub%20experience%2C%20featuring%20interactive%20challenges%20and%20games%2C%20as%20well%20as%20music%20and%20sounds.%20The%20hub%20drove%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20the%20popularity%20of%20Disney's%20songs%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Fchart-beat%2Fmitski-number-1-tiktok-billboard-top-50-disney-songs-debut-1235454060%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20entering%20the%20Billboard%20Top%2050%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAyaz%20is%20also%20preparing%20to%20create%20a%20host%20of%20new%20consumer%20touchpoints%20as%20part%20of%20The%20Walt%20Disney%20Company's%20%2460%20billion%20investment%20to%20expand%20its%20theme%20parks%20worldwide.%20And%20Walt%20Disney%20Studios%20is%20set%20to%20release%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BDeadpool%20and%20Wolverine%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20became%20the%20most-watched%20trailer%20of%20all%20time%20during%20this%20year's%20Super%20Bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrancisco%20Bram%2C%20VP%20of%20marketing%20and%20business%20development%2C%20Albertsons%20Companies%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Francisco%20Bram%2C%20VP%20of%20marketing%20and%20business%20development%2C%20Albertsons%20Companies%5C%22%20