0grocery%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBram's%20approach%20is%20ringing%20up%20results.%20In%20April%2C%20Albertsons%20reported%20same-store%20sales%20increased%201%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20digital%20sales%20increased%2022%25%2C%20and%20loyalty%20members%20increased%2016%25%20to%2039.8%20million%3B%20the%20numbers%20stand%20out%20in%20a%20year%20when%20online%20grocery%20sales%20dipped%201.2%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20according%20to%20one%20industry%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supermarketnews.com%2Fnews%2Fonline-grocery-sales-dip-12-958b-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChris%20Brandt%2C%20CMO%2C%20Chipotle%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Brandt%2C%20CMO%2C%20Chipotle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667043e9e07904901819876f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChipotle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrandt%2C%20an%20early%20adopter%20who%20embraced%20gaming%20and%20esports%20for%20Chipotle%20in%202018%2C%20saw%20an%20opening%20last%20year%20among%20the%20Fighting%20Game%20Community%20(FGC)%C2%AD%2C%20a%20gaming%20subculture%20largely%20untargeted%C2%AD%20by%20non-endemic%20brands.%20Chipotle%20gave%20away%20free%20entr%C3%A9e%20cards%20at%20the%20largest%20live%20FGC%20events%2C%20and%20used%20a%20promo%20code%20based%20on%20fan%20lingo%20to%20grant%20in-game%20currency%20to%20Street%20Fighter%206%20players.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20IRL%20and%20online%2C%20results%20were%20a%20win.%20At%20Evo%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20North%20America's%20largest%20FGC%20event%2C%20a%20crowd%20of%2010%2C000%20fans%20cheered%20ads%20from%20Chipotle%2C%20the%20first%20non-endemic%20brand%20to%20host%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20team%20tournaments%20in%20Street%20Fighter%20history.%20Through%20the%20campaign%2C%20Chipotle's%20brand%20sentiment%20score%20among%20US%20esports%20fans%20aged%2018%20to%2044%20rose%20from%2029%25%20to%2041%25%2C%20according%20to%20YouGov%20BrandIndex.%20The%20brand's%20FGC%20activations%20generated%20more%20than%201.5%20billion%20impressions%20and%20185%20earned%20media%20placements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMenu%20innovations%2C%20a%20key%20to%20consumer%20engagement%2C%20have%20been%20another%20platform%20for%20Brandt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20Chipotle%20introduced%20the%20Fajita%20Quesadilla%2C%20a%20permanent%20menu%20item%20inspired%20by%20a%20viral%20TikTok%20hack%3B%20its%20launch%20nearly%20doubled%20the%20company's%20quesadilla%20business.%20Its%20success%20led%20Brandt%20to%20create%20Chipotle's%20own%20hack%C2%AD%C2%ADs%2C%20like%20a%20sour%20cream%2FChipotle%20Tomatillo-Red%20Chili%20Sauce%20combination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20have%20been%20promising.%20The%20company's%20same-store%20sales%20rose%208.4%25%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023.%20And%20foot%20traffic%20rose%207.4%25%20in%20the%20quarter%20while%20giants%20like%20McDonald's%20and%20Starbucks%20saw%20declines%2C%20Chipotle%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandt's%20newest%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F06%2F09%2Fstyle%2Ftiktok-chipotle-portions-customers.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenge%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20a%20wave%20of%20videos%20from%20TikTokers%20who%20claim%20Chipotle's%20portion%20sizes%20have%20been%20shrinking.%20%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20no%20changes%20in%20our%20portion%20sizes%2C%20and%20we%20have%20reinforced%20proper%20portioning%20with%20our%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Chipotle%20executive%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAndrea%20Brimmer%2C%20CMO%20and%20public%20relations%20officer%2C%20Ally%20Financial%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrea%20Brimmer%2C%20CMO%20and%20public%20relations%20officer%2C%20Ally%20Financial%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667043fb764df161125a530e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAlly%20Financial%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrimmer%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20getting%20brand%20growth%20for%20Ally%20Financial%2C%20while%20pioneering%20new%20approaches%20to%20marketing%20and%20sponsorship%20that%20move%20the%20industry%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20around%202022%2C%20Brimmer%20has%20been%20driving%20positive%20change%20across%20the%20investment%20of%20brands%20in%20women's%20sports.%20This%20year%20marks%20the%20two-year%20anniversary%20of%20Ally's%2050%2F50%20pledge%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20spending%20equally%20on%20women's%20and%20men's%20sports%20by%202027.%20She%20continued%20these%20efforts%20in%202023%20with%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20media%20deal%20with%20Disney%20and%20ESPN%2C%20which%20included%20spending%20more%20than%2090%25%20on%20women's%20sports.%20In%202024%2C%20Ally%20became%20the%20official%20banking%20partner%20of%20the%20USGA%2C%20and%20both%20US%20Open%20golf%20tournaments%2C%20sponsored%20several%20women-funded%20and%20women-owned%20media%20sports%20properties%2C%20and%20worked%20with%20the%20Sports%20Innovation%20Lab%20to%20create%20the%20largest%20women's%20sports%20networking%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ally%20logo%20is%20recognized%20by%20around%20three-quarters%20of%20sports%20fans%2C%20and%20women's%20sports%20fans%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20a%2071%25%20higher%20likeability%20rate%20and%2082%25%20higher%20preference%20for%20the%20Ally%20brand%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20Brimmer%20has%20led%20Ally's%20streaming%20strategy.%20This%20included%20the%20March%20launch%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BSide%20Hustlers%26quot%3B%20reality%20series%2C%20which%20spotlights%20women%20entrepreneurs%20and%20successful%20investors.%20The%20Roku%20Channel%20series%20exceeded%20viewership%20projections%20and%20boosted%20visits%20to%20Ally.com%20by%20up%20to%2017%25.%20Ally%20also%20ran%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadage.com%2Farticle%2Fspecial-report-super-bowl%2Fally-run-streaming-only-super-bowl-ad-paramount%2F2536351%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20streaming-only%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20this%20year%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20when%20a%2030-second%20linear%20TV%20spot%20cost%20upwards%20of%20%247%20million%20%E2%80%94%20to%20emphasize%20the%20brand's%20marketing%20messages%20around%20saving%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrimmer's%20marketing%20team%20is%20also%20testing%20generative%20AI%20to%20make%20marketing%20productivity%20gains%20and%20cost%20savings.%20Using%20the%20Ally.AI%20platform's%20large%20language%20model%20chat%20and%20prompt%20functionality%2C%20a%20group%20of%20its%20marketers%20was%20able%20to%20reduce%20the%20time%20required%20to%20create%20content%20by%20up%20to%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%20and%20reported%20average%20time%20savings%20of%20up%20to%2034%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlly%20says%20that%20overall%2C%20its%20brand%20value%2C%20as%20measured%20by%20Brand%20Finance%2C%20jumped%20by%2030%25%20this%20year%2C%20while%20its%20trust%20score%20grew%20by%2010%25%2C%20a%20testament%20to%20Brimmer's%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJonnie%20Cahill%2C%20CMO%2C%20Heineken%20USA%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Jonnie%20Cahill%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20Heineken%20USA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704418764df161125a531f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHeineken%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECahill%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20moderation%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeineken%200.0%20debuted%20in%20the%20US%20in%202019%20and%20rose%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20top-selling%20nonalcoholic%20beer%2C%20with%20sales%20of%20%2477.45%20million%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Statista%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeineken%200.0%20represents%20around%207%25%20of%20the%20total%20Heineken%20franchise%20in%20the%20US%20and%20was%20the%20focus%20of%20many%20of%20the%20brewer's%20biggest%20marketing%20activations%2C%20like%20the%20Coachella%20music%20festival%20and%20major%20esports%20tournaments.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheineken-2024-nonalcoholic-sampling-push-aimed-gen-z-2023-12%5C%22%3ESampling%20was%20key%20at%20these%20events%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Heineken%20also%20debuted%20the%20lower-carb%2C%20lower-calorie%204%25%20ABV%20Heineken%20Silver%2C%20to%20appeal%20to%20drinkers%20looking%20for%20a%20lighter%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20lagers.%20It%20launched%20with%20a%20campaign%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20Taste%2C%20No%20Bitter%20Endings%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20the%20title%20sponsor%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Grand%20Prix%20in%20November.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Grand%20Prix%20activation%2C%20Heineken%20Silver%20became%20the%20first%20beer%20brand%20to%20advertise%20on%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Sphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Heineken%20devotes%2010%25%20of%20its%20global%20media%20spending%20to%20messaging%20around%20drinking%20responsibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20make%20moderation%20cool%2C%20and%20that%20will%20have%20a%20massive%20societal%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahill%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELisa%20Caputo%2C%20EVP%20and%20chief%20marketing%2C%20communications%2C%20and%20customer%20experience%20officer%2C%20Travelers%20Insurance%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lisa%20Caputo%2C%20EVP%20and%20chief%20marketing%2C%20communications%2C%20and%20customer%20experience%20officer%2C%20Travelers%20Insurance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670442d764df161125a5330%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20Insurance%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECaputo%20uses%20data%20and%20new%20platforms%20to%20keep%20the%20insurance%20company%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20helped%20launch%20the%20brand's%20first%20TikTok%20account%20that%20posts%20clips%20and%20player%20videos%20about%20the%20annual%20Travelers%20Championship%20PGA%20event.%20The%20account%20is%20currently%20promoting%20this%20year's%20upcoming%20event.%20Travelers%20also%20works%20with%20social%20and%20gaming%20creators%20to%20market%20the%20event%20to%20a%20younger%20audience%20than%20golf%20traditionally%20focuses%20on.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20six-hour%20Twitch%20livestream%20event%20raised%20about%20%2450%2C000%20for%20The%20Hole%20in%20the%20Wall%20Gang%20Champ.%20The%20livestream%20had%2041%2C000%20concurrent%20viewers%2C%20according%20to%20Travelers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELast%20summer%2C%20Caputo%20launched%20a%20campaign%20aimed%20at%20tackling%20polarization%20and%20divisiveness%20called%20%26quot%3BWho%20cares%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20campaign%20showed%20how%20many%20people%20care%20about%20issues%20like%20forest%20fires%2C%20hunger%2C%20and%20natural%20disasters.%20And%20it%20targeted%20people%20like%20public%20officials%2C%20CEOs%2C%20influencers%2C%20and%20independent%20insurance%20agents.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ECaputo's%20team%20is%20also%20using%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20to%20create%20content%2C%20including%20drafting%20articles%2C%20identifying%20audience%20groups%2C%20and%20conducting%20research.%20The%20team%20has%20developed%20tools%20that%20sales%20teams%20use%20to%20track%20marketing%20materials%20and%20monitor%20brand%20reputation%20on%20digital%20platforms%20and%20social%20media.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ECaputo%20has%20been%20in%20the%20role%20since%202011%20and%20previously%20worked%20in%20marketing%20at%20Citi.%20She%20was%20also%20previously%20a%20Deputy%20Assistant%20to%20former%20President%20Clinton%20and%20Press%20Secretary%20to%20former%20First%20Lady%20Hilary%20Rodham%20Clinton%20during%20Clinton's%20first%20term%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMarcus%20Casey%2C%20CMO%2C%20BMW%20North%20America%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Marcus%20Casey%2C%20CMO%2C%20BMW%20North%20America%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670444aed9a404d829e41cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBMW%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20center%20of%20much%20of%20BMW%20North%20America's%20marketing%20success%20this%20year%20has%20been%20the%20%26quot%3Bdata%20spine%26quot%3B%20Casey%20helped%20engineer.%20It%20connects%20customer%20data%20across%20platforms%20and%20has%20become%20a%20central%20source%20for%20BMW's%20marketing%20and%20agency%20teams%20to%20access%20insights%20and%20real-time%20analytics%20to%20see%20what's%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBMW's%202024%20Super%20Bowl%20spot%2C%20%26quot%3BTalkin'%20Like%20Walken%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20based%20on%20the%20insight%20that%20its%20%26quot%3BUltimate%20Driving%20Machine%26quot%3B%20positioning%20had%20been%20imitated%20many%20times%2C%20but%20still%20remained%20the%20ultimate.%20The%20ad%20showed%20stars%20Usher%20and%20Ashley%20Park%20imitating%20Christopher%20Walken's%20voice%20and%20cadence%20but%20ultimately%20proving%20there's%20no%20one%20else%20like%20the%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Esquire%2C%20and%20iSpot%20ranked%20it%20a%20top%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20of%202024.%20The%20continuing%20digital%20marketing%20campaign%20after%20the%20big%20game%20helped%20drive%20a%20267%25%20increase%20in%20people%20visiting%20the%20automaker's%20website%20to%20design%20their%20own%20BMW%20i5.%20Other%20programs%20included%20event%20and%20sponsorship%20integrations%20and%20the%20return%20of%20BMW's%20Ultimate%20Driving%20Experience%20tour%2C%20which%20lets%20consumers%20test-drive%20its%20EVs%20around%20a%20track.%20Sales%20of%20BMW%20EVs%20grew%2027.9%25%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202024%20to%2082%2C700.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20and%20his%20team%20are%20also%20investing%20in%20AI.%20They%20use%20Unreal%20Engine%20and%20creative%20automation%20to%20create%20personalized%20content%20at%20scale.%20The%20team%20is%20also%20using%20AI%20for%20tasks%20like%20predictive%20analytics%2C%20driving%20efficiency%20across%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEmma%20Chalwin%2C%20CMO%2C%20Workday%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Emma%20Chalwin%2C%20CMO%2C%20Workday%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704476ed9a404d829e41e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWorkday%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChalwin%20joined%20Workday%20last%20year%20after%20working%20in%20marketing%20roles%20at%20Salesforce%20and%20Adobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20tasked%20with%20explaining%20the%20cloud%20company%20to%20its%20enterprise%20clients%2C%20who%20use%20the%20technology%20to%20manage%20human%20resources%20and%20finances.%20She's%20used%20big%20branding%20campaigns%20on%20TV%20to%20reach%20B2B%20marketers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Workday's%20Super%20Bowl%20campaign%20last%20year%20that%20starred%20rock%20stars%20like%20Ozzy%20Osbourne%20and%20Joan%20Jett%2C%20Chalwin%20helped%20launch%20two%20commercials%20in%20April%20with%20a%20similar%20theme%20that%20featured%20Gwen%20Stefani%2C%20Billy%20Idol%2C%20and%20Travis%20Barker.%20The%20ads%20premiered%20during%20The%20Masters%2C%20a%20key%20time%20for%20reaching%20business%20executives.%20Within%20one%20month%20of%20launching%2C%20the%20ads%20drove%2050%25%20more%20visits%20year-over-year%20to%20Workday's%20website%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20summer%2C%20Workday%20is%20going%20on%20a%20bus%20tour%20in%2015%20cities%20to%20promote%20its%20products%20and%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternally%2C%20Chalwin%20created%20a%20program%20called%20%26quot%3BCMO%20School%26quot%3B%20that%20includes%20a%20learning%20curriculum%20and%20training%20for%20skills%20like%20upskilling%20to%20help%20marketers%20grow%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChalwin%20is%20also%20focused%20on%20AI.%20Chalwin%20uses%20AI%20to%20cut%20out%20time-consuming%20tasks%20like%20creating%20templates%20for%20campaigns%20and%20data%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKim%20Gebbia%20Chappell%2C%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20Bobbie%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kim%20Gebbia%20Chappell%2C%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20Bobbie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704487ed9a404d829e41f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBobbie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20parents%2C%20not%20just%20products%2C%20this%20direct-to-consumer%20baby%20formula%20brand%20has%20become%20the%20fastest-growing%20player%20in%20its%20category%2C%20claiming%20to%20feed%20more%20than%204.5%25%20of%20babies%20born%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChappell%2C%20chief%20brand%20officer%20since%20November%202023%20and%20a%20four-year%20Bobbie%20veteran%2C%20has%20made%20advocacy%20a%20key%20brand%20plank%2C%20positioning%20Bobbie%20as%20a%20force%20on%20issues%20including%20federal%20support%20for%20new%20parents.%20The%20company%20advised%20legislators%20on%20drafting%20the%202024%20Infant%20Formula%20Made%20in%20America%20Act%2C%20addressing%20issues%20behind%202022's%20infant%20formula%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverseen%20by%20Chappell%2C%20an%20early%202024%20partnership%20with%20tennis%20star%20Naomi%20Osaka%20brightened%20the%20brand's%20halo%2C%20launching%20a%20grant%20for%20working%20parents%20while%20campaigning%20for%20federal%20paid%20leave.%20Because%20Osaka%20had%20been%20public%20about%20her%20decision%20not%20to%20breastfeed%20daughter%20Shai%2C%20her%20choice%20as%20spokesperson%20both%20elevated%20Bobbie's%20brand%20and%20aligned%20it%20with%20mothers%20facing%20similar%20challenges.%20More%20than%2011%2C000%20parents%20applied%20for%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChappell's%20brand%20vision%20is%20getting%20results.%20With%2072%25%20revenue%20growth%20from%202022%20to%202023%2C%20Bobbie%20has%20exceeded%20%24100%20million%20in%20revenue%20and%20won%20a%20%2470%20million%20investment.%20But%20Bobbie%20may%20have%20been%20too%20successful%2C%20too%20fast%3B%20in%20January%2C%20the%20company%20paused%20online%20sales%20and%20new%20subscriptions%20until%20it%20opens%20a%20new%20manufacturing%20facility%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELee%20Anne%20Grant%2C%20chief%20growth%20officer%2C%20Babylist%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Inisder%3A%20Lee%20Anne%20Grant%2C%20chief%20growth%20officer%2C%20Babylist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667044a9ed9a404d829e4215%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBabylist%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGrant's%20job%20is%20to%20give%20soon-to-be%20and%20new%20parents%20all%20the%20information%20that%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBabylist's%20main%20offering%20is%20a%20registry%20program%20for%20managing%20shopping%20for%20baby%20products%2C%20but%20the%20site%20has%20also%20expanded%20into%20content%20such%20as%20guides%20for%20the%20best%20products%20and%20health%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Grant%20joined%20in%202020%2C%20Babylist's%20website%20traffic%20has%20increased%2025%25%20and%20reaches%20about%2010%20million%20unique%20users%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrant's%20role%20combines%20the%20CMO%20job%20with%20head%20of%20sales%20for%20Babylist's%20media%20business.%20She%20helped%20develop%20a%20content%20studio%20called%20The%20Push%2C%20where%20the%20company's%20editors%2C%20designers%2C%20and%20social-media%20team%20work%20with%20brands%20like%20Nike%20and%20Wayfair%20to%20run%20campaigns%20targeting%20Babylist's%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20for%20parents%20is%20sifting%20through%20endless%20amounts%20of%20advice%20and%20information.%20Grant%20has%20developed%20new%20ways%20to%20reach%20this%20audience%20through%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20and%20a%20physical%20showroom%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20The%20showroom%20features%20more%20than%2035%20brands%2C%20including%20Gap%20and%20Etsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Grant%20helped%20expand%20Babylist%20into%20health%20content%20with%20the%20acquisition%20and%20relaunch%20of%20Expectful.%20She%20also%20spearheaded%20a%20program%20that%20offers%20free%20breast%20pumps%20through%20insurance%20plans%2C%20and%20more%20than%2080%2C000%20breast%20pumps%20have%20been%20shipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Grant's%20leadership%2C%20Babylist%20had%20more%20than%20%24400%20million%20in%20revenue%20during%202023%20%E2%80%94%20a%2040%25%20year-over-year%20increase%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrant%20previously%20worked%20in%20brand%20and%20business%20development%20roles%20at%20The%20Assembly%2C%20Brandless%2C%20and%20PopSugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMayur%20Gupta%2C%20CMO%2C%20Kraken%20Digital%20Asset%20Exchange%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Mayur%20Gupta%2C%20CMO%2C%20Kraken%20Digital%20Asset%20Exchange%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667044bb764df161125a53aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKraken%20Digital%20Asset%20Exchange%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGupta%20has%20the%20tough%20job%20of%20getting%20consumers%20to%20trust%20crypto%20after%20the%20sector's%20quick%20boom%20and%20bust%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20subsequent%20resurgence%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20in%202022%2C%20he%20has%20used%20his%20background%20as%20CMO%20of%20brands%20like%20Gannett%20and%20Freshly%20to%20convey%20that%20Kraken%20Digital%20Asset%20Exchange%20is%20not%20only%20stable%20but%20ahead%20of%20innovation%20in%20the%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20he%20spearheaded%20Kraken's%20first%20marketing%20campaign%2C%20which%20targeted%20people%20new%20to%20crypto.%20A%20commercial%20depicts%20crypto%20as%20inspirational%20within%20the%20financial%20world.%20The%20campaign%20appeared%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20X%2C%20and%20out-of-home%20ads%20in%20places%20including%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGupta%20has%20also%20landed%20deals%20with%20creators%20like%20YouTuber%20and%20Twitch%20streamer%20KitBogg%2C%20crypto%20media%20company%20Bankless%2C%20and%20Williams%20Racing%20to%20make%20Kraken%20more%20of%20a%20household%20name.%20With%20Williams%20Racing%2C%20Kraken%20sponsors%20areas%20of%20F1%20races%20called%20Fan%20Zones%2C%20where%20the%20brand%20aims%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBrad%20Hiranaga%2C%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20Cotopaxi%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Brad%20Hiranaga%2C%20chief%20brand%20officer%2C%20Cotopaxi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667044d0e0790490181987e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECotopaxi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESustainable%20outdoor%20apparel%20brand%20Cotopaxi%20has%20described%202023%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20year%20of%20collaboration%20for%20good%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20company%2C%20in%20which%20it%20partnered%20with%20like-minded%20organizations%20that%20share%20its%20commitment%20to%20social%20and%20environmental%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20teamed%20up%20with%20HOKA%20on%20a%20sneaker%20and%20hip-pack%20collab.%20Later%20in%20the%20year%2C%20purchasers%20of%20the%20limited%20edition%20Headspace%20x%20Cotopaxi%20hip%20pack%20or%20T-shirt%20received%20a%20two-month%20Headspace%20membership%20and%20other%20exclusive%20mindfulness%20content.%20It%20also%20joined%20other%20brands%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Outdoor%20Industry%20Association%20to%20work%20with%20suppliers%20to%20reduce%20their%20emissions%20and%20advance%20research%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20efforts%20helped%20boost%20brand%20awareness%20from%2028%25%20in%202022%20to%2039.2%25%20last%20year%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20The%20company%20grew%2035%25%20and%20surpassed%20%24150%20million%20in%20sales%20in%202023.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20kept%202.75%20million%20fabric%20yards%20out%20of%20landfills%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%2C%20if%20laid%20out%2C%20would%20stretch%20from%20Miami%20to%20Boston.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContinuing%20the%20partnership%20theme%2C%20Cotopaxi%20launched%20the%20M%C3%A1s%20Vida%20trade-in%20program%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20working%20with%20Trove%20and%20Tersus%20Solutions%2C%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20swap%20and%20buy%20used%20outdoor%20gear%20and%20apparel.%20It%20also%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sltrib.com%2Fartsliving%2F2024%2F01%2F07%2Fsundance-filmmakers-will-be%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esponsor%20of%20the%20Sundance%20Film%20Festival%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20providing%20coats%20to%20jurors%20and%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJill%20Kramer%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20Accenture%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Jill%20Kramer%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20Accenture%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667044e5764df161125a53b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAccenture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKramer%20has%20led%20an%20effort%20to%20transform%20Accenture's%20marketing%20and%20communications%20function.%20She%20temporarily%20paused%20the%20team's%20output%20to%20thoroughly%20measure%20the%20impact%2C%20reach%2C%20and%20engagement%20rates%20for%20every%20asset%20and%20function%20it%20was%20producing%20using%20the%20same%20SynOps%20technology%20Accenture%20uses%20externally%20with%20clients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20huge%20efficiency%20gains.%20After%20reducing%20the%20content%20on%20Accenture.com%20by%2050%25%20and%20the%20number%20of%20pages%20on%20the%20site%20by%2045%25%2C%20users%20spent%2032%25%20more%20time%20on%20it.%20Accenture%20decreased%20social%20posts%20by%2033%25%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%2055%25%20increase%20in%20engagement.%20And%2C%20by%20implementing%20a%20universal%20content%20system%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Adobe%2C%20the%20company%20reduced%20manual%20tasks%20by%2055%25%2C%20saving%20%241.4%20million%20and%20boosting%20campaign%20performance%20by%20more%20than%2050%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKramer%20and%20her%20team%20also%20worked%20to%20position%20Accenture%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20change%20with%20its%20%26quot%3BReinvented%20with%20Accenture%26quot%3B%20global%20marketing%20campaign%2C%20which%20highlighted%20the%20company's%20work%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20she's%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccenture-cmo-jill-kramer-disability-inclusion-2023-11%5C%22%3Echampion%20of%20disability%20inclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20having%20become%20cochair%20of%20a%20new%20coalition%20designed%20to%20advance%20disability%20inclusion%20in%20the%20marketing%20and%20communications%20industry.%20Accenture%20and%20Disability%3AIN%20released%20a%20joint%20report%20that%20found%20companies%20that%20excel%20in%20their%20disability%20inclusion%20efforts%20generate%20more%20profit%20and%20revenue%20and%20are%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKramer%20has%20picked%20up%20various%20industry%20honors%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20including%20Adweek's%20B2B%20Innovation%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMarian%20Lee%2C%20CMO%2C%20Netflix%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Marian%20Lee%2C%20CMO%2C%20Netflix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667044f9764df161125a53c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20is%20the%20marketing%20force%20behind%20Netflix's%20shows%20and%20experiences.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe's%20responsible%20for%20taking%20individual%20Netflix%20shows%20and%20plugging%20them%20into%20culture%20to%20get%20consumers'%20attention.%20She's%20also%20tasked%20with%20building%20Netflix's%20brand%20amid%20big%20changes%20to%20the%20streamer%2C%20like%20the%20clampdown%20on%20password%20sharing%2C%20an%20ad-supported%20tier%2C%20and%20growing%20competition%20from%20other%20streamers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWithin%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Lee%20has%20spearheaded%20some%20of%20Netflix's%20biggest%20campaigns%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20are%20offline%20with%20activations%20and%20billboards.%20Most%20recently%2C%20Lee%20has%20been%20touting%20the%20third%20season%20of%20the%20hit%20%26quot%3BBridgerton%26quot%3B%20show%20with%20fan%20events%2C%20products%20from%20brands%20like%20International%20Delight%20and%20Williams-Sonoma%2C%20and%20sneak%20peeks%20of%20the%20show%20leading%20up%20to%20its%20premiere.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFor%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20she%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-squid-game-experience-los-angeles-review-2023-12%5C%22%3E%20launched%20an%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20where%20fans%20can%20compete%20in%20games%20inspired%20by%20the%20show.%20And%20for%20Jerry%20Seinfeld's%20%26quot%3BUnfrosted%2C%26quot%3B%20billboards%20in%20high-traffic%20areas%20like%20New%20York%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20oozed%20Pop-Tart%20filling%20with%20crumbs%20falling%20on%20cars.%20%26quot%3BUnfrosted's%26quot%3B%20ad%20campaign%20also%20included%20scratch-and-sniff%20magazine%20ads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hit%20%26quot%3BWednesday%26quot%3B%20show%2C%20a%20spinoff%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAddams%20Family%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20went%20viral%20with%20moments%20including%20actress%20Jenna%20Ortega's%20TikTok%20dance.%20Season%20two%20of%20the%20series%20is%20currently%20filming%20and%20is%20sure%20to%20get%20a%20marketing%20push%20from%20Lee%20behind%20it.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELee%20joined%20Netflix%20in%202021%20and%20was%20promoted%20to%20CMO%20in%202022%2C%20having%20previously%20worked%20at%20Spotify%20and%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGreg%20Lyons%2C%20CMO%2C%20PepsiCo%20Beverages%20North%20America%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Greg%20Lyons%2C%20CMO%2C%20PepsiCo%20Beverages%20North%20America%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670450d764df161125a53e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPepsiCo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELyons%20wants%20to%20grow%20newer%20drink%20brands%20like%20Starry%20and%20Bubly%20Burst%20while%20also%20keeping%20bigger%20brands%20like%20Pepsi%20and%20Mountain%20Dew%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20handles%20marketing%20for%20PepsiCo's%20%2428%20billion%20portfolio%20of%20beverage%20brands%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20PepsiCo's%20newest%20products%20that%20Lyons%20has%20worked%20on%20is%20Starry%2C%20a%20lemon-lime%20soda%20that%20ran%20its%20first%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20starring%20Ice%20Spice%20this%20year.%20And%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20sparkling%20water%20craze%2C%20he%20helped%20launch%20Bubly%20Burst%20%E2%80%94%20a%20line%20of%20products%20slightly%20sweeter%20than%20sparkling%20water%20with%20no%20added%20sugar.%20The%20launch%20of%20the%20product%20included%20a%20social%2C%20TV%2C%20and%20digital%20ad%20that%20played%20up%20Bubly%20Burst's%20fruit%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Mountain%20Dew%2C%20Lyons%20created%20a%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20starring%20actor%20Aubrey%20Plaza%20to%20promote%20Baja%20Blast.%20Baja%20Blast%20started%20rolling%20out%20nationwide%20this%20year%20after%20only%20being%20available%20for%20limited%20periods%20of%20time%20or%20at%20Taco%20Bell%20restaurants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20Pepsi%2C%20Lyons%20rolled%20out%20a%20new%20logo%20and%20packaging%20for%20the%20brand's%20125th%20birthday%20last%20year%2C%20including%20an%20experiential%20pop-up%20diner%20in%20New%20York%20where%20people%20could%20order%20food%20like%20Pepsi-infused%20pulled%20pork%2C%20and%20chicken%20and%20waffles%20with%20Pepsi%20butter%20and%20maple%20syrup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20taking%20on%20the%20CMO%20role%20of%20Pepsi's%20beverages%20in%20North%20America%20in%202017%2C%20annual%20sales%20have%20grown%2030%25%2C%20according%20to%20PepsiCo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKory%20Marchisotto%2C%20CMO%2C%20E.l.f.%20Beauty%20and%20president%2C%20Keys%20Soulcare%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Kory%20Marchisotto%2C%20CMO%2C%20E.l.f.%20Beauty%20and%20president%2C%20Keys%20Soulcare%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670452eed9a404d829e4263%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EE.L.F.%20BEAUTY%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMarchisotto%20has%20used%20standout%20marketing%20and%20nascent%20media%20platforms%20to%20put%20E.l.f.%20Beauty%20on%20the%20map%20in%20an%20incredibly%20competitive%20makeup%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE.l.f.%20returned%20to%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20this%20year%20with%20a%20star-studded%20cast%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%26quot%3BJudge%20Judy%26quot%3B%20Sheindlin%2C%20%26quot%3BSuits%26quot%3B%20star%20Gina%20Torres%2C%20and%20Meghan%20Trainor%2C%20among%20others%20%E2%80%94%20to%20showcase%20its%20bestselling%20%2414%20Halo%20Glow%20Liquid%20Filter.%20The%20ad%20came%20together%20in%20just%20seven%20weeks.%20Marchisotto%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glossy.co%2Fbeauty%2Fe-l-f-beauty-cmo-kory-marchisotto-on-the-brands-second-super-bowl-ad-starring-judge-judy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Glossy%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20speedy%20approach%20means%20E.l.f.%20consistently%20stays%20culturally%20relevant%20in%20its%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE.l.f.%20has%20grown%20a%20reputation%20for%20creating%20buzzy%20products%20that%20go%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Its%20unlikely%20collaboration%20with%20the%20canned%20water%20brand%20Liquid%20Death%20this%20March%20was%20no%20exception.%20The%20pair's%20limited%20edition%20%2434%20metal-inspired%20%26quot%3BCorpse%20Paint%26quot%3B%20coffin-shaped%20makeup%20set%20sold%20out%20in%2045%20minutes%20and%20delivered%2012%20billion%20media%20impressions%20within%20two%20weeks%20of%20its%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE.l.f.%20has%20leaned%20into%20newer%20platforms%20like%20Roblox%20and%20TikTok%20to%20capture%20the%20attention%20of%20younger%20consumers.%20Its%20Roblox%20game%20E.l.f.%20UP!%20has%20surpassed%2010%20million%20visits%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top-rated%20branded%20experiences%20on%20the%20platform.%20E.l.f.%20was%20also%20the%20first%20brand%20partner%20for%20a%20TikTok%20Shop%20Super%20Brand%20Day%2C%20which%20turbocharged%20its%20followers%20and%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Marchisotto's%20leadership%2C%20E.l.f.'s%20marketing%20budget%20has%20grown%20to%2022%25%20of%20net%20sales%2C%20which%20rose%2077%25%20last%20year.%20E.l.f.%20was%20the%20No.%202%20brand%20in%20the%20color%20cosmetics%20category%20in%20the%20US%20in%20March%2C%20according%20to%20Nielsen%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20top%20cosmetic%20brand%20among%20teens%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Piper%20Sandler%20Spring%202024%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESamantha%20Maltin%2C%20EVP%2C%20chief%20marketing%20%26amp%3B%20brand%20officer%2C%20Sesame%20Workshop%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Samantha%20Maltin%2C%20EVP%2C%20chief%20marketing%20%26amp%3B%20brand%20officer%2C%20Sesame%20Workshop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704558e079049018198843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESesame%20Workshop%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20leveraging%20social%20channels%2C%20live%20activations%2C%20cause%20marketing%2C%20and%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20Maltin%20is%20helping%20make%2054-year-old%20Sesame%20Workshop%2C%20its%20characters%2C%20and%20its%20IP%20as%20relevant%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20Sesame-Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20streaming%20deal%20set%20to%20expire%20next%20year%2C%20Maltin%20has%20aggressively%20amplified%20Sesame's%20profile.%20With%205.6%20billion%20global%20views%20annually%2C%20Sesame%20Street's%20YouTube%20channel%20is%20in%20the%20top%200.02%25%20of%20all%20channels%20in%20its%20category%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20Sesame's%20TikTok%20videos%20have%20drawn%2099%20million%20views.%20On%20Instagram%2C%20Oscar%20the%20Grouch%20launched%20in%20February%202024%20and%20already%20has%2048%2C500%20followers%3B%20Cookie%20Monster%20launched%20in%20November%202023%20and%20has%20153%2C000.%20Sesame's%20own%20Instagram%20Reels%20presence%20has%20seen%203%2C400%25%20surge%20in%20follower%20growth%20year-over-year%2C%20a%20rep%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Maltin's%20team%20leveraged%20a%20single%20X%20post%20from%20Elmo%20into%20a%20social-media%20phenomenon.%20With%20children's%20mental%20health%20in%20mind%2C%20%26quot%3BElmo%20is%20just%20checking%20in.%20How%20is%20everybody%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%20became%20X's%20No.%201%20trending%20topic%2C%20reaching%20218%20million%20people.%20President%20Biden%20and%20brands%20like%20Target%20joined%20the%20conversation%3B%20more%20than%20850%20media%20outlets%20covered%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrand%20partnerships%20included%20Oscar%20the%20Grouch's%20appearance%20in%20a%20United%20Airlines%20campaign%20introducing%20lower-carbon%20sustainable%20aviation%20fuel%2C%20giving%20Sesame%20IP%20a%20values-aligned%20promotional%20platform.%20And%20this%20summer%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20NBC%2C%20Sesame%20characters%20will%20broadcast%20live%20from%20the%20Olympic%20Village%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStephanie%20McCarty%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20Taylor%20Morrison%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Stephanie%20McCarty%2C%20CMO%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20Taylor%20Morrison%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670456de07904901819885f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Morrison%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20influencer%20marketing%2C%20partnerships%2C%20and%20social-impact%20efforts%2C%20McCarty%20has%20helped%20make%20the%20home-building%20brand%20Taylor%20Morrison%20top%20of%20mind%20among%20millennial%20and%20Gen-Z%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Taylor%20Morrison%20formed%20a%20partnership%20with%20The%20Home%20Edit%20cofounders%20Clea%20Shearer%20and%20Joanna%20Tepin%20from%20the%20Netflix%20Series%20%26quot%3BGet%20Organized%20with%20the%20Home%20Edit.%26quot%3B%20The%20%26quot%3BNew%20Homes%2C%20New%20Zones%26quot%3B%20content%20series%20saw%20Tepin%20and%20Shearer%20share%20tips%20for%20homeowners%20looking%20to%20organize%20their%20new%20homes.%20Taylor%20Morrison%20homeowners%20also%20receive%20a%20book%20with%20tips%20sp