20billion%20in%20box%20office%20sales%20worldwide.%20Barbie%20and%20the%20distinctive%20pink%20brand%20asset%20became%20a%20cultural%20phenomenon%20last%20summer%2C%20which%20extended%20to%20events%20like%20the%20Oscars%20that%20included%20brand%20activations%20and%20a%20memorable%20Ryan%20Gosling%20performance%20of%20%26quot%3BI'm%20Just%20Ken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20followed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketingweek.com%2Fhow-barbie-got-comfortable-being-uncomfortable-to-strengthen-its-brand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyears%20of%20work%20by%20McKnight's%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20position%20Barbie%20as%20the%20ultimate%20girl%20empowerment%20brand.%20This%20May%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Barbie%20honored%20nine%20women%20athletes%2C%20including%20tennis%20star%20Venus%20Williams%20and%20Canadian%20soccer%20player%20Christine%20Sinclair%2C%20with%20dolls%20made%20in%20their%20likenesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartnerships%20were%20a%20big%20theme%20of%20Mattel's%20marketing%20last%20year.%20McKnight's%20team%20helped%20Mattel%20collaborate%20with%20the%20NFL%20to%20launch%20official%20products%20like%20a%20Fisher-Price%20Little%20People%20Collector%20NFL%20series%2C%20American%20Girl%20NFL%20cheer%20uniforms%2C%20and%20a%20UNO%20deck%20featuring%20the%2032%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20McKnight%20will%20turn%20her%20marketing%20team%20toward%20bringing%20the%20power%20of%20Grayskull%20to%20movie%20theaters%20in%202026%2C%20when%20Amazon%20MGM%20Studios%20is%20set%20to%20release%20the%20%26quot%3BMaster%20of%20the%20Universe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVineet%20Mehra%2C%20CMO%2C%20Chime%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Vineet%20Mehra%2C%20CMO%2C%20Chime%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704599e079049018198874%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChime%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMehra%20is%20working%20to%20make%20the%20financial%20tech%20company%20a%20more%20mainstream%20name.%20The%20firm%20offers%20banking%20services%20with%20no%20monthly%20fees.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EUnder%20his%20leadership%2C%20Mehra%20requires%20that%2080%25%20of%20Chime's%20ads%20feature%20members%20to%20make%20the%20ads%20feel%20authentic%20to%20consumers.%20The%20brand's%20ads%20also%20don't%20use%20stock%20images%20or%20jargon%20about%20the%20banking%20industry%20and%20instead%20feature%20quick%20stories%20from%20users%20about%20how%20they%20use%20Chime's%20products.%20One%20ad%20highlights%20how%20direct%20deposits%20arrive%20early%20and%20a%20feature%20that%20lets%20people%20find%20nearby%20fee-free%20ATMs.%20The%20casting%20calls%20for%20these%20ads%20have%20generated%20more%20than%2056%2C000%20written%20and%206%2C000%20video%20testimonials%20since%20Mehra%20joined%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAnother%20campaign%2C%20%26quot%3BPaying%20Progress%20Forward%2C%26quot%3B%20featured%20entertainer%20Wayne%20Brady%20and%20explored%20Brady's%20financial%20journey.%20It%20generated%20368%20million%20impressions%20and%20115%20million%20video%20views.%20Chime%20has%20also%20worked%20with%20former%20NFL%20player%20Marshawn%20Lynch.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMehra's%20team%20also%20helped%20develop%20a%20card%20game%20called%20Dollars%20%26amp%3B%20Sense%2C%20which%20asks%20questions%20about%20money.%20The%20game%20was%20sold%20at%20Walgreens%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20TikTok.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMehra%20has%20worked%20at%20Chime%20since%202022%20and%20previously%20worked%20in%20marketing%20roles%20at%20companies%20like%20Good%20Eggs%2C%20Walgreens%20Boots%20Alliance%2C%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%2C%20and%20Ancestry.com.%20Some%20of%20his%20previous%20campaigns%20addressed%20issues%20like%20genetic%20testing%20at%20Ancestry%20and%20reassuring%20people%20it%20was%20safe%20to%20shop%20during%20the%20pandemic%20at%20Walgreens%20B