20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20Forrester.%20The%20mix%20is%20key%20to%20Merit%20Beauty's%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20levels%20of%20profitability%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20rep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20beauty%20business%20often%20focuses%20on%20Gen-Z%20consumers%2C%20Morin%20has%20led%20Merit%20Beauty%20to%20embrace%20older%20fans%2C%20who%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20loyal%20and%20higher-spending.%20Half%20the%20brand's%20website%20visitors%20are%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2025%20and%2045%2C%20with%20an%20equal%20share%20over%2055%20as%20under%2025%2C%20positioning%20Merit%20Beauty%20as%20a%20cross-generational%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorin's%20now%20leading%20Merit%20Beauty's%20global%20expansion.%20To%20promote%20its%20February%202023%20launch%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Morin%20relied%20solely%20on%20owned%20channels%3B%20at%20launch%2C%20one%20product%20sold%20every%2030%20seconds%20and%20averaged%20a%20nearly%206%25%20conversion%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%20triple%20the%201.9%25%20industry%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F1416169%2Fglobal-conversion-rate-health-and-beauty%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOnline%2520shopping%2520conversion%2520rates%2520for%2C2.2%2520percent%2520halfway%2520through%25202022.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EManu%20Orssaud%2C%20CMO%2C%20Duolingo%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Manu%20Orssaud%2C%20CMO%2C%20Duolingo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667045c1ed9a404d829e42ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDuolingo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20staid%20language-instruction%20category%2C%20Orssaud%20has%20elevated%20Duolingo%20with%20a%20cheeky%20brand%20identity%20that%20feeds%20off%20social-media%20notoriety%20and%20pop-culture%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuolingo's%20rotund%20brand%20mascot%2C%20Duo%20the%20Owl%2C%20has%20soared%20from%20TikTok%20fame%20to%20IRL%20stardom%20under%20Orssaud's%20creative%20direction%2C%20inserting%20itself%20into%20events%20like%20the%20Barbie%20movie%20premiere%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20concert%20tailgates%20%E2%80%95%20and%20gaining%20enormous%20visibility%20across%20platforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20avian%20influencer%20also%20starred%20in%20Duolingo's%20first%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%2C%20overseen%20by%20Orssaud.%20Themed%20around%20the%20owl's%20posterior%2C%20it%20racked%20up%20more%20than%2084%20million%20impressions.%20Likewise%2C%20an%20April%20Fool's%20campaign%20featuring%20an%20ersatz%20%26quot%3BDuolingo%20on%20Ice%26quot%3B%20musical%20scored%20more%20than%2080%20million%20impressions.%20Across%20the%20board%2C%20Duolingo's%20social-media%20impressions%20grew%20to%203%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20up%20170%25%20year-over-year%20%E2%80%95%20and%20correlating%20with%20business%20growth%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrssaud%20has%20also%20tapped%20unconventional%20partners%20to%20give%20Duolingo%20an%20edge.%20For%20its%20Japanese-language%20course%2C%20Duolingo%20aligned%20with%20Japanese%20streamer%20Crunchyroll%20to%20incorporate%20phrases%20from%20popular%20anime%20shows.%20Along%20with%20global%20press%20coverage%2C%20the%20partnership%20generated%20more%20than%2040%20million%20impressions%20across%20social%20platforms%2C%20Duolingo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20marketers%20grapple%20with%20AI's%20practical%20applications%2C%20Orssaud%20has%20applied%20the%20technology%20strategically.%20His%20team%20uses%20an%20AI-powered%20data%20scraper%2C%20built%20in-house%2C%20to%20identify%20trends%20from%20social%20comments.%20Orssaud%20has%20also%20encouraged%20Duolingo's%20brand%20group%20to%20apply%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20predict%20cultural%20moments%20for%20the%20brand%20to%20leverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERyan%20Ostrom%2C%20CMO%2C%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Ryan%20Ostrom%2C%20CMO%2C%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667045d7ed9a404d829e42fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20in%20the%20Box%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Ostrom%2C%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box%20has%20married%20pop%20culture%20with%20consumer%20research%20and%20segmentation%20to%20help%20challenge%20the%20fast-food%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box%20partnered%20with%20rapper%20Snoop%20Dogg%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BLate%20Night%20Munchie%20Meal.%26quot%3B%20The%20limited%20edition%20launch%20was%20also%20supported%20by%20a%20pop-up%20%26quot%3BDogg%20in%20tha%20box%26quot%3B%20restaurant%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20It%20became%20one%20of%20the%20brand's%20most%20successful%20campaigns%2C%20delivering%20a%2013.4%25%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20late-night%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20Munchie%20Meal%20making%20up%2020.3%25%20of%20the%20total.%20It's%20planning%20a%20follow-up%20this%20year%20with%20Ice%20Cube%20with%20a%20Chicken-Tater%20Melt%20to%20continue%20to%20promote%20the%20late-night%20eating%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContinuing%20the%20brand's%20theme%20of%20supporting%20the%20underdog%2C%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box%20looked%20to%20support%20its%20California%20community%20impacted%20by%20the%20history%20WGA%20writers'%20strike.%20The%20brand%20brought%20on%20board%20out-of-work%20horror%20screenwriters%20to%20create%20%26quot%3BFeeding%20Time%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20short%20film%20to%20promote%20the%20return%20of%20the%20brand's%20Monster%20Tacos.%20The%20campaign%20amassed%20more%20than%201%20billion%20media%20impressions%20and%20helped%20to%20sell%208.5%20million%20tacos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20product%20development%20has%20been%20key%20to%20the%20marketing%20strategy%20this%20year.%20Ostrom%20has%20also%20spearheaded%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Smashed%20Jack%2C%20the%20chain's%20first%20new%20burger%20in%20eight%20years.%20In%20just%20one%20day%2C%20the%20chain%20sold%2070%2C000%20Smashed%20Jacks%2C%20and%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20burger%20was%20sold%20out%20everywhere.%20Ostrom%20helped%20drive%20one%20of%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box's%20strongest-ever%20transaction%20weeks%20with%20the%20Mint%20Mobile%20shake%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20which%20was%20timed%20with%20St%20Patrick's%20Day.%20And%20last%20year%2C%20Jack%20in%20the%20Box%20became%20one%20of%20the%20first%20quick-service%20restaurants%20to%20begin%20selling%20a%20Boba%20tea%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJessica%20Padula%2C%20VP%20of%20marketing%20and%20head%20of%20sustainability%2C%20Nespresso%20USA%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Jessica%20Padula%2C%20VP%20of%20marketing%20and%20head%20of%20sustainability%2C%20Nespresso%20USA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667045f9764df161125a5443%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENespresso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPadula%20wants%20to%20make%20the%20coffee%20brand%20relevant%20to%20audiences%20beyond%20coffee%20lovers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20October%2C%20she%20spearheaded%20a%20live%20sports%20partnership%20with%20Netflix%20around%20the%20%26quot%3BNetflix%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20golf%20tournament%20that%20featured%20players%20from%20Netflix's%20golf%20show%20%26quot%3BFull%20Swing%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20racing%20show%20%26quot%3BFormula%201%3A%20Drive%20to%20Survive.%26quot%3B%20Nespresso's%20branding%20and%20products%20were%20integrated%20into%20the%20tournament%2C%20which%20increased%20awareness%20by%2035%25%20and%20increased%20messaging%20association%20by%2010%25%2C%20according%20to%20Nespresso.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20also%20helped%20develop%20a%20campaign%20aimed%20at%20gamers%20with%20Twitch%20streamers.%20Nespresso%20worked%20with%20influencers%20to%20show%20how%20a%20small%20coffee%20machine%20fits%20into%20Twitch's%20growing%20lifestyle%20content.%20One%20video%20from%20the%20campaign%20generated%20more%20than%203.3%20million%20impressions%20and%20was%20watched%20until%20the%20end%20by%2088%25%20of%20viewers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETargeting%20Gen%20Z%20is%20particularly%20important%20to%20Padula.%20To%20promote%20iced%20coffee%2C%20her%20team%20designed%20a%20series%20of%20mini%20caf%C3%A9%20events%20in%20places%20like%20an%20elevator%20at%20One%20World%20Trade%20Center%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Santa%20Monica's%20Pacific%20Wheel%20that%20equipped%20a%20small%20coffee%20machine%20to%20give%20out%20coffee%20and%20create%20content.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20also%20runs%20Nespresso's%20sustainability%20efforts%2C%20reflecting%20how%20younger%20audiences%20like%20Gen%20Z%20value%20social%20issues.%20Padula%20oversaw%20the%20expansion%20of%20Nespresso's%20recycling%20program%20from%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Jersey%20City%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20participation%20in%20the%20program%20has%20increased%20by%202%25%2C%20according%20to%20Nespresso.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPadula%20has%20worked%20at%20Nespresso%20for%20eight%20years%20and%20was%20elevated%20to%20the%20role%20of%20VP%20of%20marketing%20and%20head%20of%20sustainability%20last%20year.%20She%20was%20previously%20director%20of%20brand%20and%20communications%20and%20social%20media%20marketing%20manager%2C%20and%20has%20also%20worked%20in%20marketing%20roles%20at%20Swarovski%20and%20Famous%20Brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERaja%20Rajamannar%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20Mastercard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Raja%20Rajamannar%2C%20chief%20marketing%20and%20communications%20officer%2C%20Mastercard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670460fe0790490181988d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMastercard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20Leonardo%20Da%20Vinci%20marketers%20%E2%80%A6%20embracing%20the%20art%20and%20the%20science%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajamannar%20exhorted%20in%20an%20October%20op-ed%20for%20Business%20Insider.%20Rajamannar%20himself%20has%20exemplified%20that%20approach%2C%20amplifying%20Mastercard's%20far-flung%20creative%20activations%20with%20advanced%20AI%20and%20other%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20small%20businesses%20as%20a%20major%20brand%20objective%2C%20Rajamannar%20partnered%20with%20the%20social-impact%20tech%20company%20Create%20Labs%20to%20launch%20Mastercard%20Small%20Business%20AI%2C%20an%20online%20mentorship%20tool%20aimed%20at%20minority-owned%20businesses.%20Within%20Mastercard%2C%20Rajamannar%20oversaw%20the%20creation%20of%20Mastercard%20Digital%20Engine%2C%20which%20merges%20millions%20of%20data%20and%20brand%20content%20points%20into%20marcomms%20content%C2%AD%20%E2%80%95%20and%20generates%20its%20own%20media%20buying.%20Campaigns%20run%20on%20the%20platform%20have%20outperformed%20benchmarks%20by%20up%20to%2090%25%20on%20CPM%20%5Bcost%20per%20thousand%20impressions%5D%20and%20seven%20times%20on%20engagement%2C%20Mastercard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERajamannar%20also%20foresaw%20the%20post-COVID%20craving%20for%20experiences%20among%20consumers%2C%20dedicating%2070%25%20of%20Mastercard's%20recent%20marketing%20budgets%20to%20experiential%20activations.%20During%20the%202024%20Grammys%2C%20multiplatinum-selling%20artist%20SZA%20debuted%20a%20new%20song%2C%20%26quot%3BSaturn%2C%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20Mastercard%20commercial.%20The%20Grammys%20initiative%20also%20integrated%20Mastercard's%20Priceless%20Planet%20Coalition%20tree-restoration%20initiative%2C%20a%20SZA-related%20sweepstakes%2C%20and%20a%20Fortnite%20activation%20dubbed%20Restore%20the%20Forest%20Speedrun.%20The%20integrated%20campaign%20generated%20440%20million%20media%20impressions%2C%20Mastercard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20proponent%20of%20purpose-driven%20marketing%2C%20Rajamannar%20also%20led%20Where%20to%20Settle%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20platform%20that%20offered%20Ukrainian%20refugees%20guidance%20on%20work%20opportunities%20and%20home%20listings%20across%20Poland.%20The%20platform%20tailored%20recommendations%20based%20on%20data%20points%20like%20job%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAndy%20Rebhun%2C%20chief%20experience%20officer%2C%20Cava%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Andy%20Rebhun%2C%20chief%20experience%20officer%2C%20Cava%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704707e079049018198923%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECava%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERebhun%20is%20turning%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20posts%20into%20content%20that%20elevates%20the%20fast-casual%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20the%20former%20CMO%20of%20El%20Pollo%20Loco%2C%20who%20joined%20Cava%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20shortly%20before%20the%20restaurant%20chain%20went%20public%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20he%20has%20spearheaded%20Cava's%20social-media%20presence%20to%20capitalize%20on%20memes%2C%20humor%2C%20and%20ingredient-focused%20videos.%20He's%20specifically%20focused%20on%20highlighting%20user-generated%20content%2C%20including%20a%20contest%20in%20April%20that%20awarded%20three%20customers%20%245%2C000%20in%20credit%20for%20sharing%20the%20ingredients%20of%20their%20bowls%20on%20TikTok.%20The%20winners%20also%20had%20their%20bowl%20featured%20on%20Cava's%20digital%20and%20app%20menu%20as%20a%20limited-time%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERebhun%20has%20also%20improved%20Cava's%20digital-ordering%20platform%20with%20features%20like%20%26quot%3Bclick%20to%20claim%26quot%3B%20emails%20for%20customers%20to%20receive%20loyalty%20points%20and%20a%20feature%20that%20allows%20people%20to%20visualize%20building%20their%20food%20when%20placing%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava%20plans%20to%20relaunch%20its%20loyalty%20program%20this%20year.%20The%20program%20allows%20customers%20to%20collect%20points%20that%20can%20be%20redeemed%20for%20products.%20As%20third-party%20cookies%20disappear%2C%20the%20loyalty%20program%20will%20also%20give%20Cava%20more%20first-party%20data%20used%20for%20marketing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERebhun%20is%20also%20in%20charge%20of%20Cava's%20innovation%20and%20works%20with%20the%20company's%20culinary%20team%20to%20create%20new%20ingredients%20for%20its%20Mediterranean%20products.%20In%20one%20example%2C%20Cava%20tested%20grilled%20steak%20in%20the%20Dallas%20and%20Boston%20markets%20before%20rolling%20it%20out%20nationally%20this%20summer.%20Cava%20generated%20%24717%20million%20in%20revenue%20in%202023%2C%20up%2060%25%20year-over-year%2C%20and%20opened%2072%20net-new%20restaurants%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENatalie%20Sunderland%2C%20global%20head%20of%20marketing%20%26amp%3B%20communications%2Fmanaging%20director%2C%20BNY%20Mellon%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Natalie%20Sunderland%2C%20global%20head%20of%20marketing%20%26amp%3B%20communications%2Fmanaging%20director%2C%20BNY%20Mellon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704727e079049018198934%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBNY%20Mellon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESunderland%20has%20transformed%20marcomms%20for%20BNY%20Mellon%20%E2%80%94%20a%20financial-services%20giant%20that%20recently%20marked%20its%20240th%20anniversary%20%E2%80%94%20in%20just%20three%20years.%20Internally%2C%20she%20consolidated%20disparate%20teams%20into%20a%20central%20department%2C%20enabling%20more%20cohesive%20marketing%20strategies%20across%20divisions.%20Externally%2C%20Sunderland%20is%20breaking%20boundaries.%20She%20aligned%20BNY%20Mellon%20with%20community-level%20initiatives%2C%20making%20it%20first%20among%20the%20world's%2029%20G-SIBs%20(Globally%20Systemic%20Important%20Banks)%20to%20designate%20minority-%2C%20veteran-%2C%20and%20woman-owned%20firms%20as%20bookrunners%20for%20bank-note%20offerings%2C%20roles%20typically%20taken%20on%20by%20large%20global%20financial%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESunderland%20partnered%20BNY%20Mellon%20with%20New%20York%20bank%20MoCaFi%20to%20underwrite%20a%20%24500%20million%20debt%20offering%20with%20minority-owned%20firms.%20She%20also%20tapped%20BNY%20Mellon's%20Vaia%20platform%20to%20partner%20with%20MoCaFi%20on%20broadening%20payment%20options%20for%20unbanked%20people.%20To%20address%20gender%20issues%20in%20financial%20awareness%2C%20Sunderland%20forged%20an%20alliance%20with%20Poker%20Power%2C%20a%20women-led%20organization%20that%20uses%20poker%20to%20teach%20women%20confidence%2C%20decision-making%20skills%2C%20and%20risk%20assessment.%20Sunderland%20also%20helped%20launch%20SPARKS%20Shares%2C%20which%20lets%20clients%20donate%20investment%20proceeds%20to%20nonprofits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20reputational%20benefits%2C%20Sunderland's%20work%20has%20reaped%20results.%20Brand%20equity%20has%20jumped%20eight%20points%20within%2018%20months%2C%20BNY%20Mellon%20said.%20And%20the%20bank%20said%20it%20saw%20a%2030%25%20gain%20in%20sales%20wins%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDara%20Treseder%2C%20CMO%2C%20Autodesk%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Dara%20Treseder%2C%20CMO%2C%20Autodesk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704743ed9a404d829e440b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAutodesk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20Autodesk%20in%202022%2C%20Treseder%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20driving%20brand%20awareness%20for%20the%20design%20industry%20software%20company%2C%20boosting%20new%20business%2C%20and%20increasing%20customer%20satisfaction%20scores.%20Her%20efforts%20have%20helped%20Autodesk%20exceed%20its%20marketing-contributed%20pipeline%20targets%20by%2041%25%20and%20increase%20campaign%20conversion%20rates%20by%2030%25%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Treseder%20led%20five%20attention-grabbing%20brand%20activations%20that%20reached%20178%20million%20people%2C%20improved%20brand%20reach%20by%204%25%2C%20and%20boosted%20web%20traffic%20referrals%20from%20social%20media%20by%2044%25.%20Those%20included%20a%20campaign%20during%20the%20Oscars%2C%20a%20takeover%20of%20the%20Sphere%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20in%20partnership%20with%20Marvel%2C%20and%20turning%20every%20ad%20on%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20homepage%20into%20error%20messages%20that%20led%20to%20its%20State%20of%20Design%20and%20Make%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreseder%20has%20also%20been%20shepherding%20the%20launch%20of%20Autodesk's%20generative%20AI%203D-modeling%20technology.%20That's%20included%20Autodesk's%20marketing%20department%20launching%20its%20own%20internal%20generative%20AI%20tool%20that%20has%20reduced%20video%20content%20development%20time%20to%20minutes%20from%20weeks%20and%20from%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20just%20a%20few.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreseder%20has%20been%20particularly%20successful%20in%20driving%20growth%20for%20Autodesk's%20education%20business%2C%20with%20users%20increasing%20by%2020%20million%20since%20she%20joined%20the%20company.%20Autodesk%20provides%20students%20and%20educators%20with%20its%20software%20for%20free%20as%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20expand%20careers%20and%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20talent%20pool%20in%20professions%20like%20architecture%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20video-game%20design.%20The%20company%20also%20recently%20donated%20%245%20million%20to%20Howard%20University%20as%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20increase%20diversity%20in%20industries%20like%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20where%20just%203%25%20of%20engineers%20in%20the%20US%20are%20Black.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreseder%20continues%20to%20champion%20public%20health%2C%20women's%20issues%2C%20and%20diversity%20outside%20her%20work%20at%20Autodesk%20as%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Public%20Health%20Institute%20and%20her%20position%20on%20the%20board%20of%20financial%20services%20firm%20Robinhood.%20She%20also%20serves%20on%20the%20board%20of%20the%20Autodesk%20Foundation%20and%2C%20since%20joining%2C%20has%20helped%20it%20invest%20in%20eight%20organizations%20and%20startups%20that%20tackle%20problems%20ranging%20from%20labor%20shortages%20in%20South%20Africa%20to%20the%20decarbonization%20of%20building%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMassimiliano%20Tirocchi%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CMO%2C%20Trafilea%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Massimiliano%20Tirocchi%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CMO%2C%20Trafilea%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66704758ed9a404d829e4414%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETrafilea%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20six%20years%2C%2032-year-old%20Tirocchi%20has%20built%20a%20billion-dollar%20brand%20group%20with%20more%20than%2010%20million%20customers%20worldwide%20from%20Montevideo%2C%20Uruguay.%20The%20rare%20founder%20who%20doubles%20as%20CMO%2C%20Tirocchi%20has%20made%20AI%20and%20data%20cornerstones%20of%20Trafilea's%20growth%20plan%2C%20harnessing%20analytics%20to%20fuel%20both%20media%20buying%20and%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20maximize%20a%20%2470%20million%20annual%20ad%20budget%20for%20Trafilea's%20e-commerce%20brands%2C%20including%20intimates%20store%20Shapermint%2C%20skincare%20brand%20The%20Spa%20Dr.%2C%20and%20adaptogenic%20beauty%20line%20Revel%20Beauty%2C%20Tirocchi%20built%20his%20own%20AI%20platforms.%20One%2C%20dubbed%20Antares%2C%20automates%20ad%20budget%20allocation%20and%20optimization%20of%20over%20500%20campaigns%20and%2010%2C000%20ads%20annually.%20Altair%2C%20a%20second%2C%20generates%20ads%20tailored%20to%20countries%2C%20local%20slang%2C%20and%20channels.%20Trafilea%20claims%20the%20platforms%20have%20slashed%20creative%20process%20times%20by%2080%25%20and%20delivered%2010%20times%20the%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETirocchi's%20data-driven%20approach%20to%20marketing%20has%20helped%20propel%20intimates%20brand%20Shapermint%20to%20over%20%24800%20million%20in%20revenue%20and%2010%20million%20customers%20since%20its%202018%20launch%2C%20making%20it%20a%20serious%20contender%20against%20legacy%20brands%20in%20a%20fiercely%20competitive%20category.%20Three%20of%20its%20products%20are%20No.%201%20in%20their%20respective%20categories%3B%20Macy's%20and%20Walmart%20stores%20now%20carry%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETirocchi%20expects%20more%20marketing%20milestones%20for%20Trafilea%20brands%20this%20year.%20On%20tap%3A%20AI-generated%20TV%20spots%20and%20out-of-home%20ads%2C%20with%20Antares%20optimizing%20their%20budget%20and%20targeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKyle%20Watson%2C%20CMO%2C%20Celsius%20Holdings%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Kyle%20Watson%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20Celsius%20Holdings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670478d764df161125a553b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECelsius%20Holdings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Watson's%20leadership%2C%20Celsius%2C%20an%20energy%20drink%20brand%2C%20has%20grown%20from%20its%20fitness%20roots%20to%20become%20a%20broader%20lifestyle%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusic%20has%20become%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20this%20strategy.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20company%20expanded%20its%20Celsius%20Essential%20Vibes%20Tour%20to%20become%20the%20presenting%20sponsor%20of%20the%20Breakway%20multi-stop%20music%20festival.%20The%20activation%20includes%20on-site%20workouts%2C%20sampling%2C%20meet-and-greets%2C%20and%20branded%20giveaways.%20The%20beverage%20brand%20also%20held%20a%20%26quot%3BCosmic%20Desert%20party%26quot%3B%20at%20Coachella%20to%20launch%20its%20new%20Space%20Vibe%20drink%20flavors%2C%20welcoming%20celebrities%20like%20Megan%20Fox%2C%20Barry%20Keoghan%2C%20and%20Halle%20Berry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelsius%20is%20still%20very%20much%20embedded%20in%20the%20fitness%20and%20sports%20category.%20Last%20year%2C%20under%20Watson's%20marketing%20leadership%2C%20Celsius%20became%20the%20official%20sponsor%20of%20Major%20League%20Soccer%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Inter%20Miami%20CF%20team.%20She%20also%20expanded%20the%20brand's%20multi-year%20partnership%20with%20the%20Scuderia-Ferrari%20Formula%201%20team%20to%20help%20support%20Celsius's%20international%20launches%20in%20new%20markets%20like%20Canada%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelsius%20achieved%20record%20sales%20last%20year%2C%20doubling%20revenue%20and%20surpassing%20%241%20billion%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Watson's%20marketing%20and%20key%20moves%20in%20new%20product%20development%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20introducing%20new%20flavors%20in%20the%20fizz-free%20range%2C%20and%20launching%20the%20larger-volume%20Celsius%20Essentials%20line%20for%20performance%20athletes%20%E2%80%94%20helped%20it%20grow%20to%20become%20the%20No.%203%20energy%20drink%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20an%2011.5%25%20market%20share%2C%20according%20to%20Circana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBen%20Webley%2C%20CMO%2C%20Scopely%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Ben%20Webley%2C%20CMO%2C%20Scopely%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667047a7764df161125a554f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScopely%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%