cording%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESherry%20Weiss%2C%20CMO%2C%20Dow%20Jones%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CMO%20Insider%3A%20Sherry%20Weiss%2C%20CMO%2C%20Dow%20Jones%20and%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667047c2ed9a404d829e447f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDow%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWeiss%20is%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20media%20organization's%20marketing%20that%20spans%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20MarketWatch%2C%20and%20Barron's.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe's%20tasked%20with%20promoting%20the%20media%20group%20to%20advertisers%20and%20clients%2C%20as%20well%20as%20consumers.%20Last%20year%2C%20she%20hired%20three%20new%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20Mother%2C%20Mediahub%2C%20and%20TBWA%20Worldwide%20%E2%80%94%20to%20shake%20up%20its%20advertising.%20In%20one%20example%2C%20a%20campaign%20called%20%26quot%3BMissing%20Articles%26quot%3B%20featured%20a%20blank%20front%20page%20of%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20to%20remind%20the%20public%20about%20reporter%20Evan%20Gershkovich%2C%20who%20has%20been%20detained%20by%20Russia%20since%202023.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHer%20marketing%20efforts%20have%20also%20helped%20increase%20news%20subscribers%20from%202.43%20million%20in%202019%20to%205.7%20million%20as%20of%20the%20fiscal%20third%20quarter.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20also%20oversees%20marketing%20for%20the%20professional%20services%20arm%2C%20which%20includes%20Dow%20Jones%20Risk%20Compliance%2C%20Dow%20Jones%20Energy%2C%20and%20Factiva.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20most%20recently%20rolled%20out%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20brand%20campaign%20promoting%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal's%20new%20newsroom%20structure%20under%20editor-in-chief%20Emma%20Tucker.%20The%20campaign%20aims%20to%20broaden%20the%20publisher's%20business%20readership.%3Cbr%3E