%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fppsv7468_palace_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20MLA%20Ganta%20Srinivas%20Rao%20led%20an%20NDA%20delegation%20and%20the%20media%20in%20the%20first-ever%20tour%20of%20the%20lavish%20%26quot%3Bpalace%20on%20the%20hill%26quot%3B%20overlooking%20a%20beach%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20excursion%20left%20everyone%20stunned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRZ%20(Coastal%20Regulatory%20Zone)%20clearance%20was%20given%20by%20the%20central%20government%20in%20May%202021%20for%20a%20tourism%20project%20to%20be%20developed%20on%20Rushikonda%20Hills%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP's%20national%20general%20secretary%20Nara%20Lokesh%2C%20however%2C%20says%20Jagan%20Reddy%20decided%20to%20use%20it%20exclusively%20as%20his%20camp%20office%20and%20built%20it%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20500%20crore%20from%20the%20state%20exchequer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rushikonda%20palace%20is%20spread%20over%20a%209.88-acre%20sea-facing%20site.%20Ganta%20Srinivas%20Rao%20said%20the%20previous%20government%20had%20built%20it%20in%20secrecy%2C%20using%20public%20funds%20on%20luxurious%20amenities%2C%20high-quality%20furnishing%2C%20sparkling%20chandeliers%2C%20bathtubs%20and%20the%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flqf20ko8_palace-1_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20compared%20the%20extravagance%20to%20palaces%20built%20by%20Iraq%20dictator%20Saddam%20Hussein%20and%2C%20closer%20home%2C%20Gali%20Janardhan%20Reddy.%20The%20%26quot%3Bpalace%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20includes%20a%20large%2