s--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fsbi-plans-to-raise-rs-10000-cr-via-infrastructure-bonds-say-bankers-124061800377_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fsbi-plans-to-raise-rs-10000-cr-via-infrastructure-bonds-say-bankers-124061800377_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zyn%2C%20already%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20pauses%20selling%20nicotine%20pouches%20online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ZYN%20nicotine%20cases%20and%20pouches%20are%20seen%20on%20a%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce4a49a610a9069d594e81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContainers%20of%20Zyn's%20nicotine%20pouches.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZyn%20has%20stopped%20online%20sales%20after%20receiving%20a%20subpoena%20from%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDC%20banned%20flavored%20tobacco%20products%2C%20including%20nicotine%20pouches%2C%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnline%20sales%20make%20up%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bvery%20small%26quot%3B%20share%20of%20overall%20sales%2C%20Zyn's%20parent%20company%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EZyn%2C%20which%20was%20already%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-nicotine-pouches-out-stock-shortage-new-york-jersey-florida-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshort%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20stores%2C%20could%20get%20tougher%20to%20buy%20after%20the%20company%20halted%20online%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20the%20popular%20nicotine%20pouch%20said%20the%20company%20received%20a%20subpoena%20from%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia's%20attorney%20general%20about%20sales%20of%20flavored%20products.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EZyn's%20flavors%20include%20peppermint%2C%20cinnamon%2C%20and%20citrus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlavored%20tobacco%20products%2C%20including%20flavored%20nicotine%20pouches%2C%20have%20been%20banned%20in%20DC%20since%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZyn%20parent%20company%20Philip%20Morris%20International%20said%20it%20intends%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20subpoena.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20preliminary%20investigation%20indicates%20that%20there%20have%20been%20sales%20of%20flavored%20nicotine%20pouch%20products%20in%20D.C.%2C%20predominantly%20related%20to%20certain%20online%20sales%20platforms%20and%20some%20independent%20retailers%2C%26quot%3B%20PMI%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmi.com%2Fmedia-center%2Fpress-releases%2Fpress-details%2F%3FnewsId%3D27856%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bmaterial%20liability%20is%20reasonably%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Zyn.com%20sales%20make%20up%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20small%26quot%3B%20share%20of%20nationwide%20sales%20volumes.%20In%20February%2C%20PMI%20said%20that%20it%20shipped%20nearly%20385%20million%20cans%20of%20pouches%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%2062%25%20higher%20than%20its%202022%20shipments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZyn%20produces%20two%20%26quot%3Bunflavored%26quot%3B%20varieties%20called%20Smooth%20and%20Chill%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20advertised%20as%20%26quot%3BFlavor%20Ban%20approved%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20website.%20It%20is%20unclear%20if%20these%20two%20varieties%20are%20allowed%20for%20sale%20in%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20flavored%20tobacco%20bans%20are%20also%20in%20place%20in%20California%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPMI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20standard%20business%20hours.%20Zyn's%20website%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20restart%20shipments%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20coming%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2F