%2Famericas%2Fcrime%2Fdr-benjamin-brown-pensacola-florida-plastic-surgeon-b2564333.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20day%20Ms%20Hillary%20went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20she%20was%20scheduled%20to%20undergo%20miniature%20muscle%20plication%2Fabdominal%20scar%20revision%2C%20bilateral%20arm%20liposuction%2C%20lip%20injections%2C%20and%20ear%20adjustment%20procedures.%20She%20reportedly%20prepared%20her%20own%20anaesthesia%20before%20the%20surgeries.%20She%20also%20ingested%20a%20handful%20of%20multicoloured%20pills%2C%20including%20Valium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20the%20procedures%2C%20she%20began%20experiencing%20symptoms%20relating%20to%20sedation.%20When%20she%20went%20into%20the%20operating%20room%2C%20her%20husband%20administered%20additional%20anaesthesia%20without%20being%20able%20to%20verify%20what%20his%20wife%20took.%20He%20subsequently%20did%20not%20record%20his%20wife's%20medication%20and%20dosage.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20his%20wife%20told%20him%20that%20her%20vision%20was%20becoming%20blurry%20and%20she%20saw%20%26quot%3Borange%26quot%3B.%20Moreover%2C%20she%20experienced%20restlessness%2C%20muscle%20twitching%20and%20blurred%20vision%20which%20are%20common%20symptoms%20of%20toxicity.%20The%2041-year-old%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20injecting%20drugs%20into%20her%20face%2C%20following%20which%20she%20became%20unresponsive%20and%20started%20to%20seize.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Findian-astrologer-stands-by-prediction-claims-world-war-3-is-days-away-5913389%5C%22%3EIndian%20Astrologer%20Stands%20By%20Prediction%2C%20Claims%20World%20War%203%20Is%20Days%20Away%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20a%20medical%20assistant%20asked%20the%20doctor%20if%20they%20should%20call%20emergency%20services%20and%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20next%2020%20minutes%2C%20th