%20feet%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20successful%20modern%20romance%2C%20a%20new%20survey%20has%20revealed.%C2%A0The%20study%2C%20conducted%20by%20Talker%20Research%20and%20commissioned%20by%20Seeking.com%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20evolving%20landscape%20of%20romantic%20expectations%20among%20Americans.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F06%2F17%2Flifestyle%2Fwhat-is-hypergamy-the-dating-trend-40-of-americans-do%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Esurvey%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%202%2C000%20US%20adults%2C%20conducted%20between%20May%2024%20and%20May%2028%20this%20year%2C%20revealed%20interesting%20insights%20into%20what%20constitutes%20a%20%26quot%3Bluxurious%26quot%3B%20dating%20experience%20today.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EKey%20findings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CLuxury%E2%80%9D%20in%20modern%20dating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnForty-seven%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20consider%20learning%20about%20their%20date's%20background%20and%20engaging%20in%20intelligent%20conversations%20as%20luxurious.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-nine%20per%20cent%20believe%20it%20is%20luxurious%20for%20their%20date%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20entire%20outing.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EImportance%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bswept%20off%20their%20feet%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSixty-five%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20find%20it%20important%20to%20feel%20%26quot%3Bswept%20off%20their%20feet%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20successful%20romantic%20encounter.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-five%20per%20cent%20believe%20the%20relationship%20is%20doomed%20if%20they%20don't%20feel%20swept%20off%20their%20feet%20on%20a%20first%20date.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EAttractive%20traits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEighty%20per%20cent%20find%20self-confidence%20attractive.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSeventy-five%20per%20cent%20are%20attracted%20to%20people%20who%20are%20proud%20of%20their%20life%20accomplishments.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSeventy-three%20per%20cent%20like%20people%20who%20go%20above%20and%20beyond%20on%20a%20first%20date.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnForty-two%20per%20cent%20find%20financial%20stability%20and%20cooking%20skills%20to%20be%20the%20most%20attractive%20traits.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHaving%20a%20nice%20home%20(24%25)%2C%20a%20cultured%20taste%20in%20music%20(21%25)%2C%20and%20a%20good%20fashion%20sense%20(20%25)%20are%20also%20highly%20attractive%20qualities.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EViews%20on%20Hypergamy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnForty-five%20per%20cent%20believe%20it%20is%20acceptable%20to%20showcase%20their%20success%20and%20wealth%20on%20a%20first%20date.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-one%20per%20cent%20consider%20financial%20success%20attractive.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-nine%20per%20cent%20believe%20finding%20a%20partner%20who%20exhibits%20hypergamic%20traits%20contributes%20significantly%20to%20personal%20growth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20hypergamy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFrom%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Real%20Housewives%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20%3Cem%3EBridgerton%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20notion%20of%20marrying%20into%20higher%20social%20ranks%20has%20always%20interested%20people.%20This%20trend%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bhypergamy%2C%26quot%3B%20involves%20families%20climbing%20the%20social%20ladder%20through%20strategic%20marriages%2C%20a%20concept%20as%20old%20as%20time%20itself.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHypergamy%20is%20the%20act%20of%20marrying%20or%20dating%20someone%20perceived%20as%20more%20successful%20or%20secure.%20Whether%20done%20consciously%20or%20subconsciously%2C%20it%20often%20stems%20from%20a%20desire%20for%20financial%20security%2C%20reputation%20enhancement%C2%A0or%20seeking%20higher%20self-worth%20and%20identity.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20concept%20has%20gained%20attention%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20but%20hypergamy%20has%20historical%20roots%20dating%20back%20centuries.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEmma%20Hathorn%2C%20in-house%20dating%20and%20relationships%20expert%20at%20luxury%20dating%20site%20Seeking.com%2C%20says%20that%20people%20seek%20meaningful%20connections%20with%20partners%20who%20share%20their%20intellect%20and%20ambitions%20in%20life.%20%E2%80%9CShowcasing%20those%20ambitions%20and%20treating%20dates%20to%20a%20taste%20of%20luxury%20sets%20the%20bar%20for%20the%20relationship%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Hathorn%20remarked.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CPeople%20want%20to%20find%20themselves%20elevated%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20the%20conversation%20itself%20and%20by%20being%20treated%20to%20something%20tailored%20to%20them%2C%20exclusively%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718693220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-05%2F7fg8esmg_couple-dating-generic_625x300_05_May_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsurvey-reveals-what-americans-consider-essential-in-modern-romance-5913993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sixty-five%20per%20cent%20of%20Americans%20believe%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bswept%20off%20their%20feet%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20successful%20modern%20romance%2C%20a%20new%20survey%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsurvey-reveals-what-americans-consider-essential-in-modern-romance-5913993%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsurvey-reveals-what-americans-consider-essential-in-modern-romance-5913993%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsurvey-reveals-what-americans-consider-essential-in-modern-romance-5913993%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWasn't%20Able%20To%20Hear..%26quot%3B%3A%20Alka%20Yagnik%20Diagnosed%20With%20Rare%20Hearing%20Disorder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.