%20Chinese%20billionaires%20have%20similarly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-64781986%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evanished%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213a80849-31f9-4b0a-9021-b6faf916e547%5C%22%3ELoyalty%20to%20China%20under%20scrutiny%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Shein's%20public%20face%20has%20been%20executive%20chairman%20Donald%20Tang.%20The%20Shanghai-born%20businessman%2C%20who%20became%20a%20US%20citizen%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20moved%20up%20the%20ranks%20at%20now-defunct%20investment%20bank%20Bear%20Stearns%20and%20joined%20Shein%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20speech%20Tang%20gave%20underscores%20the%20careful%20tightrope%20all%20Chinese%20executives%20walk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20Xu%20may%20be%20staying%20out%20of%20public%20view.%20At%20the%20Milken%20Institute%20last%20month%2C%20Tang%20said%20Shein's%20roots%20are%20Chinese%2C%20while%20its%20headquarters%20make%20it%20Singaporean%2C%20but%20its%20ethos%20is%20American.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETang's%20attempt%20to%20pacify%20officials%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Pacific%20attracted%20significant%20attention%20in%20Beijing.%20The%20company%20is%20still%20waiting%20for%20officials%20to%20greenlight%20its%20application%20to%20list%20outside%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20raises%20questions%20of%20loyalty%20to%20China%20that%20some%20in%20Beijing%20find%20uncomfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20listing%20issue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F6ecb58d1-2582-48ae-8503-773b228da57e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20Financial%20Times%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Chinese%20business%20writers%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20Shein%20pressured%20them%20to%20skip%20writing%20about%20Tang's%20apparent%20gaffe%2C%20and%20the%20Milken%20Institute%20removed%20a%20video%20of%20the%20speech.%20The%20group%20did%20not%20immediately%20