he%20associate%20teams%20about%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20surprise%20that%20this%20person%20targeted%20a%20player%20from%20the%20Ugandan%20national%20team.%20Associate%20nations%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20big%20teams%2C%20are%20soft%20targets%20for%20corruption%20but%20in%20this%20case%20the%20player%20who%20was%20approached%20did%20the%20needful%20by%20informing%20the%20ICC%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20report%20a%20corrupt%20approach%20is%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20ICC's%20anti-corruption%20code.%20The%20other%20offences%20include%20match-fixing%2C%20betting%20on%20the%20game%2C%20misuse%20of%20inside%20information%20and%20failing%20to%20co-operate%20with%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUganda%20ended%20their%20T20%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20with%20a%20memorable%20win%20over%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20and%20losses%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20the%20West%20Indies%20in%20Trinidad%20on%20Friday.%20Uganda%2C%20first-timers%20in%20the%20competition%20alongside%20Canada%20and%20co-hosts%20USA%2C%20played%20three%20of%20their%20four%20league%20games%20in%20Guyana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlayers%20are%20approached%20all%20the%20time%2C%20more%20so%20from%20smaller%20nations.%20In%20bigger%20events%20like%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20there%20is%20more%20scrutiny%20and%20if%20an%20approach%20is%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ICC%20ACU%2C%20then%20due%20protocol%20is%20followed%20and%20a%20proper%20investigation%20is%20conducted%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20effect%20from%20June%201%2C%20the%20ICC%20tweaked%20its%20anti-corruption%20code%20to%20empower%20the%20governing%20body%20and%20its%20member%20boards%20to%20%26quot%3Bto%20proactively%20and%20thoroughly%20investigate%20incidents%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20ongoing%20effort%20to%20protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20anti-corruption%20code%20covers%20all%20cricket%20(whether%20international%20or%20domestic)%20played%20under%20the%20auspices%20of%20the%20ICC%20and%20its%20Members%20and%20applies%20to%20all%20Participants%3B%20player%2C%20coach%2C%20trainer%2C%20manager%2C%20selector%2C%20team%20owner%20or%20official%2C%20doctor%2C%20physiotherapist%2C%20match%20referee%2C%20pitch%20curator%2C%20player%20agent%2C%20umpires%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ICC%20and%20NCF%20Officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20are%20bound%20by%20the%20Code%20for%202%20years%20after%20they%20have%20last%20participated%20in%20any%20form%20of%20official%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20maximum%20possible%20sanction%20for%20the%20most%20serious%20breaches%20of%20the%20Anti-Corruption%20Code%20is%20a%20life%20ban%20from%20all%20involvement%20in%20the%20game.%20In%20some%20countries%2C%20there%20is%20also%20the%20possibility%20of%20criminal%20sanctions%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20an%20extract%20from%20ICC%20anti-corruption%20code%20for%20participants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20international%20players%20are%20regularly%20briefed%20about%20a%20potential%20threat%20and%20are%20well-versed%20with%20the%20anti-corruption%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorrupt%20approaches%20at%20big%20ticket%20events%20are%20not%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%2C%20Canada's%20then%2020-year-old%20wicket-keeper%20Hamza%20Tariq%20was%20approached%20by%20alleged%20bookmakers.%20He%20duly%20reported%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718690700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbc1rm6_uganda-cricket-afp_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fmatch-fixing-at-t20-wo