li%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20homes%20cost%20the%20Japanese%20property%20market%20some%20%2424.7%20billion%20over%20five%20years%20through%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJapan%20has%20been%20offering%20these%20abandoned%20homes%20at%20throwaway%20prices%20to%20lure%20buyers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-ghost-towns-population-vacancy-rates-akiya-banks-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglut%20of%20abandoned%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20akiya%20%E2%80%94%20has%20hit%20the%20prices%20of%20surrounding%20properties%2C%20and%20the%20damage%20goes%20into%20the%20tens%20of%20billions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FBusiness%2FMarkets%2FProperty%2FJapan-s-abandoned-houses-wipe-25bn-off-nearby-property-value%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20by%20Nikkei%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20estimated%20that%20the%20country's%20property%20market%20suffered%20losses%20of%20some%20%2424.7%20billion%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%20due%20to%20the%20falling%20property%20values%20of%20homes%20near%20derelict%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20quoted%20research%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.j-akiya.jp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%20Akiya%20Consortium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20group%20of%2014%20companies%20and%20a%20research%20institution%20that%20aims%20to%20tackle%20Japan's%20akiya%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20consortium's%20research%2C%20land%20prices%20for%20properties%20within%20a%20165-foot%20radius%20of%20the%20akiya%20are%20cratering.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20due%20to%20various%20factors.%20For%20one%2C%20potential%20buyers%20concerned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.japantimes.co.jp%2Feditorials%2F2024%2F05%2F03%2Fjapan-abandoned-buildings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetation%20overgrowth%20and%20pest%20infestations%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20abandoned%20homes%20are%20steering%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPest%20infestations%20aside%2C%20the%20houses%20can%20also%20pose%20serious%20safety%20hazards.%20Poorly%20maintained%20properties%2C%20for%20one%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Fajw%2Farticles%2F15082632%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20collapse%20in%20earthquakes%2C%20landslides%2C%20or%20extreme%20weather%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20akiya%20also%20can't%20be%20occupied%20or%20demolished%20without%20tracking%20down%20the%20original%20owner%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time-consuming%20exercise%2C%20as%20descendants%20may%20have%20moved%20away%20or%20become%20uncontactable.%20As%20such%2C%20these%20houses%20have%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20%26quot%3Bghost%20villages%26quot%3B%20in%20Japan's%20rural%20prefectures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20government%20is%20offering%20incentives%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapanese-government-selling-rural-homes-cheap-akiya-banks-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeap%20%24500%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tax%20reliefs%2C%20to%20entice%20residents%20to%20move%20from%20urban%20areas%20back%20to%20rural%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeigners%20have%20jumped%20on%20the%20deals%2C%20snagging%20large%20properties%20for%20low%20prices%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-abandoned-houses-renovations-dream-homes-akiya-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenovating%20them%20into%20their%20dream%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Chris%20McMorran%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Japanese%20Studies%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20(NUS)%2C%20told%20BI%20in%202021%20that%20the%20outlook%20for%20rural%20communities%20remains%20bleak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20empty%20houses%20is%20a%20blight%20on%20the%20landscape%2C%20and%20a%20further%20deterrent%2C%20because%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20terminal%20village%20surrounded%20by%20'ghost%20houses%2C'%26quot%3B%20McMorran%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-ghost-towns-population-vacancy-rates-akiya-banks-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20to%20Insider's%20Lina%20Batarags%20and%20Cheryl%20Teh.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan'a%20akiya%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fmay%2F01%2Fakyia-houses-why-japan-has-nine-million-empty-homes%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Nomura%2520Research%2520Institute%2520estimates%2Cof%2520houses%2520within%2520a%2520decade.%26amp%3Btext%3DMore%2520than%25204.4m%2520of%2Cfrom%2520the%2520main%2520population%2520centres.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eballooned%20to%20nine%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%20October%202023%2C%20accounting%20for%20nearly%2014%25%20of%20all%20homes%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20number%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20as%20Japan's%20population%20shrinks%2C%20ages%2C%20and%20moves%20from%20rural%20to%20urban%20dwellings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAkiya%20also%20includes%20abandoned%20condominiums.%20According%20to%20Nikkei%2C%20owners%20who%20leave%20their%20homes%20and%20don't%20pay%20the%20condominium%20management%20and%20maintenance%20fees%20could%20lower%20the%20value%20of%20the%20building%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20estimate%20was%20limited%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20abandoned%20single-family%20houses%20on%20land%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Teppei%20Kawaguchi%2C%20CEO%20of%20Crassone%2C%20a%20construction%20and%20demolition%20services%20company%20that%20heads%20the%20consortium%2C%20told%20Nikkei.%20%26quot%3BThe%20actual%20negative%20impact%20may%20be%20even%20greater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20flip%20side%20to%20this%20property%20crisis.%20While%20buyers%20may%20be%20shying%20away%20from%20purchasing%20homes%20around%20akiya%2C%20some%20abandoned%20homes%20have%20caught%20the%20fancy%20of%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-moving-buying-abandoned-homes-japan-let-foreigners-own-home-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanting%20to%20buy%20cheap%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Japanese%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20November%2C%20Airbnb%20told%20Nikkei%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-millions-empty-home-akiya-ghost-houses-tourism-airbnb-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewants%20to%20partner%20with%20local%20governments%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20encourage%20homeowners%20to%20renovate%20their%20abandoned%20homes%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20be%20used%20as%20tourist%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20a%20good%20source%20of%20income%20after%20people%20retire%20as%20our%20lifetime%20gets%20longer.%20If%20the%20owners%20of%20idle%20assets%20refurbish%20them%20and%20convert%20them%20into%20lodgings%2C%20that%20would%20be%20a%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20Airbnb's%20head%20of%20Japan%2C%20Yasuyuki%20Tanabe%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FBusiness%2FTravel-Leisure%2FAirbnb-looks-to-convert-Japan-s-empty-homes-into-tourist-lodgings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENikkei%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrassone%2C%20a%20construction%20and%20demolition%20services%20company%20that%20heads%20the%20consortium%2C%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-akiya-abandoned-homes-property-market-bleeding-billions-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718689294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b015196c8f0a134f7951e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-akiya-abandoned-homes-property-market-b