%20own.%20Exporting%20was%20an%20alien%20concept%20for%20them%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20to%20sell%2C%20the%20payment%20mechanism%2C%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20exports%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Krushal%E2%80%99s%20assistance%20in%20securing%20customer%20orders%2C%20finding%20airline%20slots%2C%20processing%20fruit%20meeting%20the%20stringent%20quality%20requirements%20of%20the%20export%2C%20export%20processing%20and%20documentation%2C%20and%20custom%20clearance%20management%2C%20farmers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20make%20five%20to%20six%20shipments%20and%20exported%20about%2010%20tonnes%20of%20produce%20to%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20and%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20launched%20their%20website%20aamore.co.in%20for%20online%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20of%20this%20effort%20has%20been%20very%20encouraging%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20level%20of%20customer%20delight%20and%20the%20demand%20for%20more%20shipments%20from%20trade%20partners%20and%20consumers%20alike.%20The%20FPC%20expects%20to%20expand%20its%20export%20activities%20multi-fold%20in%20the%20next%20year%20based%20on%20the%20experience%20gained%20and%20the%20brand%20traction%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6f2Z6RR3cN%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6f2Z6RR3cN%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2F