ges%20deter%20them%20from%20living%20their%20best%20lives%20and%20adopting%20their%20son%2C%20who%20they%20now%20call%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20light%20of%20their%20lives%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrivatsan%20and%20Saravanan%20went%20through%20a%20year-long%20process%20and%20spent%20over%2060%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%20to%20legally%20adopt%20Sendhan%20as%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20the%20journey%20like%20for%2045-year-old%20Srivatsan%3F%20How%20did%20he%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20being%20gay%20and%20navigating%20life%20when%20his%20parents%20wanted%20him%20to%20marry%20a%20girl%2C%20no%20matter%20what%3F%20From%20trying%20to%20take%20his%20own%20life%20to%20being%20out%20and%20proud%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20his%20incredible%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Choosing%20myself%20helped%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20his%20early%20childhood%2C%20Srivatsan%20knew%20that%20he%20was%20different.%20He%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20with%20his%20cousin%20sisters%20than%20his%20brothers.%20His%20first%20crush%20was%20on%20a%20blue-eyed%20boy%20with%20curly%20hair.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hated%20playing%20cricket%20in%20the%20hot%20sun%2C%20especially%20fielding%3B%20this%20was%20my%20first%20clue.%20Also%20I%20just%20always%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20something%20different%20about%20me.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20relate%20to%20the%20boys%20in%20class%20and%20over%20time%2C%20I%20understood%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294409%2Fi-am-gay-brothers-ashish-vishesh-chopra-coming-out-story-raksha-bandhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20was%20gay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201195px)%20100vw%2C%201195px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2