CThis%20whole%20process%20only%20takes%2030%20to%2045%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20industries%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20has%20also%20made%20forays%20into%20the%20residential%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20continuous%20expertise%20for%20regular%20operations%20as%20well%20as%20guidance%20on%20the%20needed%20retrofits%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20their%20STP%20completely%20streamlined%20and%20treat%20and%20reuse%20their%20water.%20We%20have%20converted%20many%20residential%20STPs%20from%20dysfunctional%20to%20reusing%2070%25%20of%20water%20in%20flushing%2C%20horticulture%2C%20and%20more.%20Many%20customers%20used%20to%20receive%20notices%20and%20fines%20from%20the%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20earlier%20because%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20manage%20their%20operations%2C%20and%20we%20have%20solved%20that%20for%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAdaptable%20to%20different%20environments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20software%20is%20highly%20flexible%2C%20featuring%20comprehensive%20configuration%20panels%20that%20simplify%20the%20integration%20of%20plants%20of%20different%20sizes%20and%20technologies.%20On%20the%20backend%2C%20we%20have%20onboarded%20each%20key%20unit%20operation%20in%20water%20management%2C%20be%20it%20biological%20treatment%2C%20chemical%20treatment%2C%20RO%20systems%2C%20UF%20systems%20or%20more%2C%20so%20when%20we%20onboard%20a%20new%20unit%2C%20we%20simply%20tick%20that%20module%20and%20get%20the%20relevant%20analytics%2C%20automation%20flows%2C%20alerts%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20adapt%20to%20facilities%20of%20all%20kinds.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20team%20is%20well-equipped%20to%20provide%20expert%20support%20for%20any%20plant%20management%20as%20required.%20For%20instance%2C%20at%20present%2C%20we%20serve%20diverse%20needs%20including%20STP%20man