20way%20vegetables%20are%20grown.%20These%20specially%20designed%20bags%20require%20only%20two%20litres%20of%20water%20to%20nourish%20the%20plants%20effectively%2C%20making%20them%20not%20only%20water-efficient%20but%20also%20cost-effective.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20innovative%20design%20of%20these%20grow%20bags%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%2C%20ensuring%20healthier%20plant%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20these%20durable%20grow%20bags%20could%20be%20significant%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agriculture%20practices.%20By%20reducing%20water%20usage%20and%20enhancing%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20grow%20materials%2C%20these%20bags%20represent%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20solving%20some%20of%20the%20persistent%20challenges%20in%20vegetable%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20organic%20journey%20leading%20to%20a%20patented%20grow%20bag%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%20was%20first%20introduced%20to%20organic%20farming%20while%20still%20in%20Malabar%2C%20where%20he%20experimented%20with%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20determine%20what%20worked%20best%20for%20various%20crops.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20he%20expanded%20his%20organic%20farming%20practices%20to%20include%20livestock.%20On%20his%20three-acre%20farm%2C%20cows%20and%20goats%20coexist%20with%20vegetables.%20He%20notes%20that%20cow%20dung%20serves%20as%20an%20excellent%20fertiliser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20consuming%20the%20vegetables%20that%20were%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Reading%20about%20the%20ill%20effects%20of%20consuming%20food%20with%20pesticides%20prompted%20me%20to%20start%20growing%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eyyo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296470%2Faward-winning-kerala-terrace-farmer-grows-s