%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20lived%20there%20with%20his%20army.%20The%20Maharana%20of%20Udaipur%20had%20issues%20with%20a%20troublesome%20tribe%20in%20the%20area%20where%20we%20now%20live%2C%20in%20Bisalpur.%20This%20area%20was%20on%20the%20border%20between%20Jodhpur%20and%20Udaipur%20at%20that%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Maharana%20instructed%20my%20ancestor%2C%20Rao%20Haridasi%2C%20to%20suppress%20these%20rivals.%20He%20successfully%20conquered%20the%20land%2C%20and%20in%201705%2C%20this%20territory%2C%20comprising%2024%20villages%2C%20was%20granted%20to%20my%20family%2C%20making%20us%20direct%20subjects%20of%20the%20Maharana.%20Since%20then%2C%20from%201705%20onwards%2C%20my%20family%20has%20resided%20in%20this%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20property%20has%20evolved%20over%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20pictures%2C%20you%20will%20notice%20a%20distinctive%20white%20building%20with%20Indo-European%20architecture%2C%20built%20in%201938%20by%20my%20great-grandfather.%20This%20architecture%20is%20unique%20compared%20to%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20styles%2C%20which%20often%20feature%20intricate%20%3Cem%3Ejharokhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(overhanging%20enclosed%20balconies)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejaali%3C%2Fem%3E%20(latticework)%20designs.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20haveli%20was%20restored%20keeping%20intact%20the%20original%20structure%20and%20design.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-